src: re gopola bašomedi ba rena ba tlhokomelo ya maphelo vukuzenzele unnamed palo ya moragorago ya mahu a go hlolwa ke coronavirus e fetile 2 000. godimo go bao ba lobilego maphelo a bona ke bašomedi ba tša maphelo, ditsebi tša go hloka bosodi mešomong ya bona bao ba hlokometšego bao ba lwalago, ebile e be e le bona ba thekgago le go homotša bao ba lego maokelong ba beetšwe thoko le ba malapa a bona.
tgt: kubonga lokukhetsekile lokucondziswe kutisebenti tetfu tekunakekela ngetemphilo vukuzenzele unnamed linani lalabashone ngenca yeligciwane lecorona esikhatsini lesisandza kwendlula selengce sibalo se2 000. emkhatsini walabo labalahlekelwe timphilo tabo tisebenti tekunakekela ngetemphilo, tingcweti letiphelele lebetinakekela labagulako, futsi betitinsika futsi tidvudvuta labo labasesibhedlela labahlukanisiwe nemindeni yabo.

src: gore banna le basadi bao ba rwelego mošomo wo o bohlokwa wa go kgethega magetleng a bona ke bona bao ba fetelwago ke bolwetši bjo le go hlokagala ke taba ye hlobaetšago kudu.
tgt: indzaba yekutsi lamadvodza nabomake labenta lemisebenti lehloniphekile nalengcwele kwabona bayagula futsi bayashona kusishayo lesibuhlungu kakhulu.

src: ke bona batho ba matho mothomo ba go phenkgišana le leuba le.
tgt: ngibo labayibambe embi li lapho imphi yekulwa nalolubhubhane ishisa khona.

src: ba šoma ka tlase ga kgatelelo ye kgolo ebile ba swanela ke go dula ba tshwenyegile megopolong ka ge ba tseba gore ba kotsing ya go fetelwa ke baerase ye.
tgt: basebenta ngaphasi kwekucindzeteleka lokukhulu futsi kufanele kutsi batfwale kucindzeteleka ngekwengcondvo ngobe bati kutsi basebungotini bekutseleleka ngaleligciwane.

src: ke bagale le bagalegadi ba makgonthe ba phenkgišano ya rena kgahlanong le coronavi rus.
tgt: bangema chawekati nemachawe sibili emphi yetfu yekulwa naleligciwane lecorona.

src: re hlompha bagale ba ba maafrika borwa bao ba tlogelago magae a bona, malapa a bona le baratwa ba bona gore ba tle mešomong tšatši ka tšatši ntle le go šitwa ba eya dikliniking, maokelong le mafelong a mangwe a tša maphelo.
tgt: sibatfulela sigcoko labantfu baseningizimu afrika labanesibindzi labashiya emakhaya abo, imindeni kanye nalababatsandzako kutsi baye emsebentini ngaphandle kwekuphutsa onkhe malanga emitfolamphilo, etibhedlela kanye nakuletinye tikhungo tetemphilo.

src: gona fao ba fana ka tlhokomelo ya bongaka, thekgo ya tša tsamaišo le ditirelo tše dingwe go swana le go hlwekiša le go fepa batho ka dijo.
tgt: lapho bafike banike kunakekela kwetekwe lashwa, kwesekela ngetekuphatsa kanye naletinye tinsita letifanana nekuhlanta kanye nekuphakela ngekudla.

src: ge ba le gare ba phethagatša mešomo ya bona ya bokgoni, le rena bjalo ka setšhaba ke mošomo wa rena go ba šireletša le ba malapa a bona.
tgt: njengaloku nabo benta umsebenti wabo webungcweti, natsi kanjalo sinemsebenti lekumele kutsi siwente kubo kanye nasemindenini yabo.

src: maphelo le polokego ya bona a swanetše go tla pele.
tgt: imphilo yabo kanye nekuphepha kwabo kufanele kutsi kube ngulokusemcoka kakhulu.

src: re a ba hlompha le go ba thekga bjalo ka banna le basadi bao ba laeditšego gore ba itokišeditše go bea maphelo a bona kotsing gore re tle re kgone go phela.
tgt: siyabahlonipha futsi siyabatisa njengabobabe nabomake labakhombise kutsi ba timisele kubeka timphilo tabo ebungotini kute kutsi tsine siphile.

src: gore ba kgone go dira mešo mo ya bona ye boimaima ba hloka thekgo le tšhireletšo ya rena ka kabo ya didirišwa tša tšhireletšo ya mmele (dippe).
tgt: kute kutsi bente umsebenti wabo lomkhulu bayakudzinga kutsi sibasekele kanye nekutsi sibavikele ngekutsi sibanike tisetjentiswa tekutsi bativikele bona (ippe).

src: ka thekgo ya sekhwama sa naga le dineelano tša go tšwa go maafrika borwa a mantši o tee ka o tee, dikgwebong, dithe ong le mebušong ye mengwe, re ile ra kgona go rekela bašomi ba ba bogale dippe.
tgt: ngekwesekelwa sikhwama semfelandzawonye kanye neminikelo levela kulabo bantfu labanengi baseningi zimu afrika, emabhizinisi, tinhlangano kanye nalabanye bohulumende, sikhonile kutsi sitsenge tisetjentiswa tekuvikela letisebenti letinesibindzi letisebenta embili lapho kunebungoti khona.

src: fao go bilego le tlhaelelo ya dippe, maokelo a rena a hlaganela seemo seo ka ponyo ya leihlo go netefatša gore didirišwa tšeo di ba gona.
tgt: lapho kube nekuswelakala kwetisetjentiswa tekutivikela (emappe) tibhedlela tetfu tiya kulungisa ngekushesha loko kuci nisekisa kutsi tiyatfolakala.

src: re tseba gore khumanego ya dippe ga se yona tlhotlo e le noši yeo bašomedi ba tša maphelo ba lebaganego le yona.
tgt: siyati kutsi kukhona ku finyelela kutfola tisetjentiswa tekutivikela akusiyo kuphela insayeya tisebenti tetfu tekunakekela ngetemphilo letibukene nayo.

src: go ralala naga ka bophara, dikliniki le maokelo di lebagane le tlhaelelo ya bašomi.
tgt: kuyo yonkhe imitfolamphilo yalelive kanye netibhedlela tibukene nekuswelakala kwetisebenti.

src: bothata bjo bo gare bo a hlaganelwa.
tgt: lenkinga isasonjululwa.

src: go thekga mošomo wo bašo medi ba rena bao e lego ba mathomo ba go lwantšha bolwetši bjo ba o phethagatšago nageng ka bophara re romela ditona le batlatšatona seleteng se se nngwe le se se nngwe sa ka mo nageng go utolla ditlhotlo tša fao go ya ka fao batho ba itemogelago tšona dileteng tšeo le go šoma mmogo le makgotlataolo a profense a tša maphelo.
tgt: kwesekela lomsebenti lowentiwa tisebenti tetfuletisebenta ebungotini kulolonkhe lelive sitfumela tindvuna kanye nemasekela etindvuna kuleso naleso sigodzi kulelive titibonele tinkinga letitsite kuleto tigodzi kanye nekutsi tisebentisane netiphatsimandla tetemphilo tetifundza.

src: re swanetše go šoma mmogo go šireletša maphelo a bohle e sego fela a bašomedi ba tša maphelo eupša a bašomedi ka moka.
tgt: kudzingeka kutsi sisebente kanye kanye kute sigadze hhayi kuphela timphilo tetisebenti tetfu letisebenta ebungo tini kodvwa tonkhe tisebenti.

src: go šetše go bile le mošomo wa bothakga wo dirilwego ke diyunione go ruta maloko a tšona ka taolo ya go fetelwa ke bolwetši le thibelo gotee le tlhweko.
tgt: kunemsebenti lomuhle kakhulu losewentiwe tinyonyana ekufundziseni emalunga eveni lonkhe mayelana nekulawula kusuleleka kanye nekuvikeleka kanye nekuhlanteka.

src: tšona diyunione tše di thekga gape mošomo wa kgoro ya mešomo le ya bašomi go swara ditekolo tša mafelo a mešomo go netefatša gore ditshepedišo tša maphelo le tša polokego di a hlongwa go bašomedi bao ba boelago mešomong.
tgt: tiphindze futsi tisekele umsebenti welitiko letekucashwa nemisebenti ekubambeni imihlanganosikolwa yekuhlola kucinise kisa kutsi kunekugcinwa kwetinchubo tetemphilo nekuphepha letikhona taleto tisebenti letibuyako.

src: tše ntši tša diyunion e tša bašomi le tšona di fana ka tshedimošo ya coronavirus go maloko a tšona mola bengmešomo ba le gare ka masolo a temošo.
tgt: tinyonyana tetfu letinengi tiphindze futsi tinike lwatiso lweligciwane lecorona kumalunga ato kantsi nebacashi banemikhankhaso labayentako yekucaphelisa.

src: ye nngwe ya dihlotlo tšeo di hlagetšego naga ya gaborena ke ka fao batho bao go hlatsetšwego gore ba nale coronavirus ba tlontlollwago ka gona.
tgt: yinye yetinsayeya lebonakele kulelive letfu kubandlululwa kwalabo bantfu labatfolakale kutsi banaleligciwane lecoro na.

src: bjalo ka setšhaba, re nale maikarabelo a mohlakanelwa a go fediša go tlontlollwa ga batho bao ba fetetšwego ke coronavirus .
tgt: njengemmango, sinesibo pho sonkhe ngekuhlanganyela kutsi sikucedze nya lokubandlululwa kwebantfu labasuleleke ngaleligciwane lecoro na.

src: go bile le dipego tše hlobaetšago tša ka fao batho ka noši ba hlomarwago go tšwa fao ba tšwago le batho setšhabeng bao ba ipelaetšago kgahlanong le balwetši ba coronavirus ge ba amogelwa maokelong le dikiliniking tša kgauswi le bona.
tgt: kunemibiko letsikametako yebantfu labakhishwa umkhomboloti emimangweni yabo kanye nemimango leshucela tigulane letineligciwane lecorona letingeniswe etibhedlela tendzawo kanye nasemitfolamphilo.

src: se se swanetše go fela.
tgt: loko kufanele kutsi kuphele.

src: go swana le ka fao re bilego ngatana ye tee go hlohleletša go amogelwa ga batho bao ba nago le hiv le go ema ka lentšu le tee go lwantšha hlaolo ya bona, re swanetše go laetša kwešišo, kgotlelelo, boleta, kwelano le kwelobohloko go bao ba fetetšwego ke baerase ye le ba malapa a bona.
tgt: njengaloku sihlangana ekugcugcuteleni kwemukelwa kwalabo labaphila neligciwane lehiv futsi sime sicine simelane nekuhlukunyetwa, kufanele kutsi sikhombise kuvisisa, kwemukelana, umusa, kuvelana kanye nekucabangela labo labasuleleke ngaleligci wane kanye nemindeni yabo.

src: gothwe maitshwaro a a go tlontlollwa ga batho a hlohleletšwa ke poifo ya go fetelwa ke bolwetši le go hloka kwešišo.
tgt: kutsiwa kubandlululana kugcugcutelwa kwesaba kwesuleleka ngesifo kanye nekweswela kuvisisa.

src: tsela ye kaonekaone ya go fenya poifo ya rena ya tlhago ya bolwetši bjo le ya go fetelwa ke go latela ditshepedišo tša hlweko tšeo di lego gona.
tgt: indlela lencono kakhulu yekuncoma kwesaba kwetfu kugula kanye nekutsatselana kutsi sigcine tinchubo tekuhlanteka letibekiwe.

src: poifo ya go fetelwa ke bolwetši go hlatsetšwe gore e gona ebile ke ya makgonthe.
tgt: kwesaba kwesuleleka kunesizatfu lesivakalako futsi kuliciniso.

src: go le bjalo, re tseba seo re swanetšego go se dira go itšhireletša le go šireletša ba bangwe.
tgt: ngalokufananako, siyati kutsi yini lekumele kutsi siyente kute sitivikele futsi sivikele nalabanye.

src: re tseba gore baerasee ye e hlolwa ke eng le gore re ka dira eng go itšhireletša gore re se fetelwe.
tgt: siyati kutsi yini lokubange la leligciwane nekutsi yini lesingakwenta kute sitivikele kutsi singatseleleki.

src: re tseba gabotse gore re swanetše go šielana sekgala, go ipeela thoko le batho ba bangwe ge re kopane le bao ba fetetšwego le go ihlagiša maokelong ge re nale dika tša bolwetši bjo.
tgt: siyati kutsi kufanele kutsi sichelelane ngekwenhlalo, sihlale sodvwa nangabe kwenteke satsintsana nalabo labasulelekile kanye nekutsi siye esibhedlela nangabe sinetimphawu letikhomba kwesuleleka.

src: re swanetše go tšwelapele go hlahlwa ke dintlha tša mannete e sego mabarebare.
tgt: kufanele kutsi sichubeke siholwe ngemaciniso hhayi emahemuhemu.

src: nako yela ya gore mang le mang a bolele gore yena ga a tsebe motho yo a fetetšwego goba a amilwego ke coronavirus e fetile kgale.
tgt: sikhatsi sekutsi utsi ababati umuntfu losulelekile nome lotsintsekile ngaleligciwane lecorona sesendlule kudzala.

src: ka nako ye, go feta mehla yohle, bagwera ba rena, ba malapa, bašomimmogo le baagišane ba hloka kwelobohloko le thekgo ya rena.
tgt: nyalo, kakhulu kunakucala, bangani betfu, imindeni yetfu, lesisebenta nabo kanye nabomakhelwane badzinga luvelo lwetfu kwanye nekubasekela.

src: mo matšatšing, dibekeng le dikgwedi tše tlago, re tla fela re ikhwetša re hloka tshepho le go boifa ge re bona palo ya bao ba fetetšwego le bao ba hlokagalago e hlatloga.
tgt: kulamalanga, emaviki kanye netinyanga letitako, ngaletinye tikhatsi sitawukutikhandza sesiphelelwe litsemba futsi sesesaba nasibona emanani ebantfu labasulelekile kanye nalabo labashonako achubeka ngekwenyuka.

src: go ka direga gore seemo se gakale, eupša re nale bonnete bja gore go tla kaonafala.
tgt: kungenteka kutsi tintfo tibe timbi kakhulu, kodvwa sinesiciniseko sekutsi sitawubancono.

src: boramahlale ba rena le baeletši ba dingaka ba re boditše gore kelo ya diphetelo e tla hlatloga ge re batamela nhlorwaneng ya rena ya diphetelo.
tgt: bososayensi betfu kanye nebaluleki betekwelapha baseluleka ngekutsi lizinga lekusuleleka litakwenyuka njengaloku sisondzela esicongweni setfu.

src: eupša nnete ke gore palo ye e tla theogela fase.
tgt: kodvwa nakanjani litawuphindza futsi lehle.

src: re gopola bašomedi ba rena ba tša maphelo bao ba lobilego maphelo a bona ba hlokometše balwetši.
tgt: sibonga leto tisebenti letinakekela ngetemphilo letilahlekelwe timphilo tato ngekunakekela labagulako.

src: molemi wa moswa o amogela thekgo ya covid19 silusapho nyanda molemi yo a sa thomago tša temo wa kua kapa bohlabela ke yo mongwe wa bao ba holegilego go tšwa sekhwameng sa mmušo sa kimollo ya coronavirus.
tgt: umlimi lomncane utfola lusito lwecovid19 silusapho nyanda umlimi losafufusa wasempumalanga kapa ungulomunye walabazuzile esikhwameni selusito lweligciwane lecorona sahulumende.

src: nomagcinandile suduka wa mengwaga ye 27 o aga bohwa bja lapa la gabo le lehumo ka go beeletša temong.
tgt: nomagcinandile suduka (27) ukhu lisa ligama nemno tfo wemndeni wakubo ngekusisa kutekulima.

src: mong wa kgwebo ya 4 u and 4 me primary cooperative kua motsaneng wa mooiplaas o amogetše thušo go tšwa sekhwameng sa kimollo sa coronavirus (covid19) sa kgoro ya temo, mpshafatšo ya naga le tlhabollo ya dinagamagae ka baka la polasa ya gagwe, ya mae gagwe, diruiwa le merogo.
tgt: umnikati we4 u and 4 me primary cooperative esigodzini sasemooip laas watfola kwesekelwa lokuvela kusikhwama selusito lweligciwane lecorona (covid19) selitiko letekulima, lekubuyiselwa kwemhlaba nelekutfutfukisa tindzawo tasemakhaya selipulazi lakhe lemacandza, lemfuyo nelemifino.

src: kgoro e fane ka dibaotšhara tša go bitša r1.2 bilione go balemi bao ba di hlokago.
tgt: litiko likhiphe emavawu sha lalingana r1.2 emabhili yoni kubalimi labanesidzingo.

src: suduka o bolela gore di baotšhara di tla mo thuša go godiša lehlakore la kgwebo ya gagwe la go tšweletša mae.
tgt: suduka utsi ivawusha yakhe itamsita kutsi akhulise incenye yelibhizinisi lakhe lekukhicita emacandza.

src: "ke amogetše dibaotšhara tše tharo tša go bitša r19 000. tšona ke baotšhara ya r12 000 go reka dikgogo tša go bea mae tse 100, baotšhara ya r6 500 ya go reka dijo tša dikgogo le baotšhara ya r500 ya go reka meryana.
tgt: "ngatfola emavawusha lamatsatfu elinani selilonkhe lelir19 000. ivawusha yelinani lelir12 000 yekutsenga tinkhukhu letitalela emacandza leti100, ivawusha yelinani lelir6 500 ye kutsenga kudla nevawusha yer500 yekutsenga imitsi.

src: "o thomile polasa ya gagwe ya go tšweletša dikgogo ka go fepa dikgogo tša gae tša lapa la gabo ka dijo tša go di thwathwadiša mae, tšeo di di kgontšhago gore di thwathwatše mae ntle le gore di namelane.
tgt: "wacala lelipulazi lakhe lekukhicita emacandza ngekunika tinkhukhu takubo tendzabuko kudla lokukhulisa kutalela emacandza, lo kutenta tikhicite emacandza ngaphandle kwekuhlangana nelichudze.

src: dikgogo tša gagwe gabjale di tšweletša mae a 50 ka letšatši, gomme yena o wa rekiša beke ka beke.
tgt: tinkhukhu takhe leti50 nyalo tikhicita emacandza la50 ngelilanga, lawatsengisa njalo ngeliviki.

src: suduka, yo le yena a tsenetšego tša temo ka dipudi tše 73, dinku tše 25 le dikgomo tše 25 o thomile tša temo ka 2015 morago ga go ikhweletša sethifikeithi sa n6 sa taolo ya mmušo go tšwa kholetšeng ya ikhala ya thutatiro le ya tlhahlo.
tgt: suduka, lobuye abe ngu mlimi wetimbuti leti73, timvu leti25 netinkhomo leti25, wacala kuba ngumlimi ngemnyaka we2015 emva kwekutfola sitifiketi sen6 sepublic management lasitfola eikhala training and vocational education and training college.

src: morago ga go lemoga gore mešomo ga e kaalo, a tšea sephetho sa go tšea polasa yeo ka nako yeo e bego e dirišwa ke lapa la gabo go iphediša a e fetošetša go ba kgwebo ya go dira letseno.
tgt: emva kwekubona kutsi kute ematfuba ekutfola umsebenti, watsatsa sincumo sekutsatsa lipulazi lakubo lebelilima kancane waligucula labalibhizinisi lelinenzuzo.

src: suduka ge a bolela o re: "re gotše re dira tša temo, ke moka morago ga go aloga ke tšeere sephetho sa go tsenela temo legatong la go inyakela mošomo."
tgt: suduka utsi: "sikhule senta umsebenti webulimi, ngakoke emva kwekutfola ticu ngitsetse sincumo sekuba ngumlimi kunekutsi ngibuke umsebenti.

src: se se ile sa hlatsela go ba sephetho sa hlohleletšo, kudu ka ge a godišitše dipudi le dikgomo tša palo ya go bonagala.
tgt: "loku kube sincumo lesikhutsatako, njengoba bekasakhulise timbuti netinkhomo letinengi.

src: polasa ya suduka ya di hektara tše tshela ka bogolo e tšweletša mafela, matapola, dierekise le dinawa.
tgt: sivandze sasaduka lesi mahektha lasitfupha sikhicita ummbila, emazambane, emaphizi nemabhontjisi.

src: mafela a bjalwa dihektareng tše nne, matapola a bjalwa hektareng ye tee mola dierekisi le dinawa di bjalwa mo hektareng ya mafelelo.
tgt: ummbila uhlanyelwe kumahektha lamane, emazambane kuhektha yinye kwatsi emaphizi nemabhontjisi abelana ngehektha yekugcina.

src: suduka o ithutile tše ntši go tšwa go covid19 , kuduku du ka gore thoto ye kaoneka one ke matsogo a gagwe le go šoma ga gagwe ka thata.
tgt: suduka ufundze lokunyenti kucovid19 , kakhulu kutsi lokubaluleke kakhulu ngiletandla takhe nekusebenta kwakhe ngekutikhandla.

src: go aga bophelo bjo bokaone vukuzenzele unnamed go tšwa motsaneng wa kwanongoma gola kwazulunatal fao a goletšego gona ka go itshokolela, silondiwe magwaza wa mengwaga ye 23 o hlotše mapheko a mantši gore a fihlelele toro ya gagwe ya go ba molaodi wa tša kago.
tgt: kwakha likusasa lelincono vukuzenzele unnamed umuntfu lotitfobile lobekangasilutfo lobuya esigodzini sakwanongoma, kwazulunatal, silondiwe magwaza loneminyaka le23 wancoba tihibe letinengi kute aphumelelise liphupho lakhe lekuba ngumphatsi wetekwakha.

src: mananeokgoparara a go fokola ao magwaza a gotšego a bona go potologa fao a bego a dula gona a mo file hlohleletšo ya go inyakela ditsela tše diswa tša go kaonafatša setšhaba sa gabo.
tgt: kukhula abona sakhiwonchanti lesingasisihle kwakhutsata magwaza kutsi abuke tindlela letinsha tekuphakamisa ummango wakhe.

src: ga bjale ke yena wa mathomo ka lapeng la gabo wa go ikhweletša tikrii.
tgt: nyalo nguye wekucala lomsikati emndenini wakhe kutfola ticu.

src: magwaza o phethile dithuto tša gagwe tša mošomo wo wa tša kago go tšwa yunibesithing ya witwatersrand ka 2019, a ikhweletša tikrii ya mathomo ya dithuto tša kago.
tgt: magwaza watfola ticu takhe eyunivesithi yasewitwatersrand ngemnyaka we2019, watfola ticu tekucala tetifundvo tetekwakha.

src: "kwanongoma e nale mana neokgoparara a go fokola kudu ebile kabo ya ona e bonagala e sepela ka go nanya kudu.
tgt: "ikwanongoma inesakhiwonchanti lesizingeni le liphansi futsi kuphakelwa kwaso kubonakala kuhamba ngesivinini lesincane kakhulu.

src: ka go lebelela ditlhotlo ka moka tšeo toropo ya gešo e lebaganego le tšona, ke ile ka ba le hlohleletšo ya go dira se sengwe sa go amana le tša kago gore ke kgone go ba yo mongwe wa bao ba fetošago seemo sa bjale," a realo.
tgt: kubuka tonkhe tinsayeya letibukene nelidolobhatsi, kwangigcugcutela kutsi ngente lokutsite lokumayelana netekwakha kute ngibe ngilomunye webantfu labatawugucula lesimo lesikhona nyalo," usho njalo.

src: go hwetša lengwalo la gagwe la thuto go be go se bonolo.
tgt: kutfola ticu takhe bekungasiyo intfo lemalula.

src: magwaza o bolela gore go be go le boima kudu gore a bee kgopolo ya gagwe dithutong ka baka la ge a be a dula a belaetšwa ke go hloka thekgo ya ditšhelete.
tgt: magwaza utsi bekulikhuni kubeka wonkhe umcondvo wakhe etifundvweni ngenca yekuhlala akhatsatekile ngemali.

src: ke moka a thušwa ke kemedi ya thekgo ya mananeokgoparara a mmasepala (misa).
tgt: ngaleso sikhatsi, iejensi yekusekela sakhiwonchanti samasipala (misa) yangenelela yamsita.

src: "ke be ke dula ke gatelegile kudu mogopolong ka gobane ke gotše ga boima go tloga bonyenyaneng.
tgt: "bengivame kukhatsateka kakhulu mayelana nemali njengoba ngiphuma emndenini lobewuncishwe ematfuba.

src: tshokolo yaka e fedile ka 2018 ge ke be ke amogela pasari go tšwa misa.
tgt: kwate kwaba ngumnyaka we2018, lapho ngatfola khona umfundzate lokhishwa yimisa.

src: se se nkhotše go phethagatša lengwalo la ka la tikrii ntle le gore ke gatelege mogopolong gape.
tgt: loku kwangisita kuphotfula ticu tami ngaphandle kwekukhatsateka.

src: dithuto tšaka ka moka di be di lefetšwe, nna ke be ke šaletšwe fela ke gore ke bee šedi yaka ka moka dithutong tšaka," a realo.
tgt: tonkhe tifundvo tami takhokhelwa, konkhe bekufuneka ngikwente kugcila etifundvweni tami," usho njalo.

src: magwaza ke wo mongwe wa baithuti ba makgolokgolo bao ba fetago matsogong a misa ka mananeo a ngwaga ka ngwaga a tlhabollo ya baswa.
tgt: magwaza ungulomunye we bafundzi londlule kutinhlelo temisa tekutfutfukisa lusha njalo ngemnyaka.

src: mananeo a a fana ka thušo ya tšhelete le ka thekgo ebile a thuša baithuti gore ba ikhwe letše dikgoba tša mešomo ge ba fihleletše maswanedi a mošomo dithutong tša bona.
tgt: letinhlelo tinika imali nekwesekelwa futsi tincedza titjudeni kutsi titfole kubekwa emsebentini uma setitfole ticu.

src: "ke be ke tloga ke emetše monyanya wa rena wa dikalogo.
tgt: "bengiwulangatelele kakhu lu umcimbi wetfu wekwetfweswa ticu.

src: e be e tlaba monyanya wo mogolo kudu ka ge ke be ke tla ba motho wa mathomo wa go aloga ka lapeng la gešo.
tgt: bewutawuba yintfo lenkhulu uma ubuka kutsi bengitawuba wekucala kuba neticu emndenini.

src: ke sa ntše ke holofela gore re ka ba le letšatši la rena la go aloga, eupša go ka direga gore se se folotše go lebeletšwe leuba la coronavirus ,’’ a realo.
tgt: ngi sanelitsemba lekutsi sitawuba nalomcimbi, kodvwa loku kungahle kungenteki ngenca yalobhubhane weligciwane lecorona ," usho njalo.

src: intasteri ya tša kago e tletše kudu ka banna.
tgt: imboni yetekwakha igcwele kakhulu emadvodza.

src: "ka nako tše dingwe, basadi ba ikwa ba nyenyefaditšwe ka gobane bokgoni ba bona ba go tliša diphetogo bo fela bo belaelwa.
tgt: "letinye tikhatsi, bomake bentiwa kutsi bative babancane ngenca yekutsi likhono labo lekuletsa luntjintjo luyangatjatwa.

src: ka nako tše dingwe mantšu a bona ga a theeletšwe.
tgt: letinye tikhatsi livi labo alilalelwa.

src: "gontše go le bjalo ke kgeth ile taolo ya tša kago ka gobane ke dumela gore ke nale maatla a go fetoša intasteri ye le go e kaonafatša fao go nyakegago gona.
tgt: "nanyalo ngisakhetsa kuba ngumphatsi wetekwakha ngoba nginelitsemba lekutsi nginemandla ekugucula lemboni futsi ngiyitfutfukise lapho kunesidzingo khona.

src: ke bone basadi ba bangwe intastering ye ba nyologela maemong a god imo ebile ba nale khuetšo.
tgt: ngibone bomake kulemboni bakhuphukela etikhundleni letisetulu futsi baba nemandla ekugucula tintfo.

src: ke dumela gore le nna nka nyologela maemong a a godimo,’’ a realo.
tgt: ngiyatsemba kutsi nami ngitawuphumelela," usho njalo .

src: bjalo ka sealoga sa mathomo ka lapeng la gabo, silondiwe magwaza o leboga misa.
tgt: ngekuba wekucala emndenini wakhe kutfola ticu, silondiwe magwaza ubonga imisa.

src: afrika borwa e tšea kgato ya go rarolla bothata bja tlhokego ya dithušagohema silusapho nyanda sethušagohema seo se dirilwego ka mo afrika borwa se tla thuša balwetši bao ba nago le dika tša magareng tša covid19 gore ba heme gabonolo.
tgt: iningizimu afrika itsatsa sinyatselo sekulungisa kuswelakala kwetisitakuphefumula silusapho nyanda sisitakuphefumula lesakhiwe kulelive sitawusita tigulane letinetimphawu letingasimatima kakhulu tecovid19 kutsi tiphefumule lula.

src: ntwa kgahlanong le bolwetši bja coronavirus (covid19) ka afrika borwa e matlafaditšwe ke sethušagohema sa mathomo seo se dirilwego ka mo nageng.
tgt: kulwa nesifo seligciwane lecorona (icovid19) lapha eningizimu afrika kufakwe umfutfo sisitakuphefumula sekucala lesentiwe lapha kulelive lakitsi.

src: sethušagohema sa continuous positive airway pressure (cpap) se thuša balwetši bao ba nago le dika tša magareng tša covid19 gore ba kgone go hema gabonolo ka go ba fa moya wa oksetšene gore o dire gore meelamoya ya bona e dule e bulegile.
tgt: lesisitakuphefumula lesatiwa ngekutsi pheceleti continuous positive airway pressure (icpap) sisita tigulane letinetimphawu letingasimatima kakhulu tecovid19 kutsi tiphefumule lula ngekutsi sitinike umoyamphilo losezingeni lelilingene lesicindzetelo semoya kute kugcineke emaphayiphi lahambisa umoya avulekile.

src: sethušagohema se hlamilwe ke ba council for scientific and industrial research (csir) ka tšhomišano le e tšwelapele letlakaleng la 2o boloke afrika borwammogo re ka fenya coronaviruso bolokeg batšeakarolo ba se bakae ba mo gae, gomme e tla abelwa balwetši go phatlalala le naga bao ba nago le mathata a go hema mo legatong la mathomo la phetelo ya covid19.
tgt: lesisitakuphefumula sadizayinwa ngumkhandlu wetesayensi netelucwaningo lwetetimboni (icsir) ngekuhlanganyela nebalingani bakuleli labanengi futsi sisatjalaliswa eveni lonkhe sisetjentiswe tigulane letikhombisa kuba nenkinga ekuphefumuleni esigabeni sekucala sekuhabula icovid19.

src: "moya woo motho ao hemago o na le dipersente tše 23 tša oksetšene.
tgt: "umoya lotayelekile umuntfu lawuphefumulako unemoyamphilo lowetiye ngemaphesenti lange23.

src: sethušagohema sa cpap se kgona go pompa oksetšene e ntšhi, gomme ya thuša motho go hema.
tgt: impampi yesisitakuphefumula yecpap ingampompa linani lelisetulu lemoyamphilo, kusita umuntfu kutsi aphefumule.

src: cpap e pompa oksetšene e sa emiše.
tgt: icpap impompa ngalokuchubekako umoyamphilo lotiyile.

src: o ka oketša goba wa fokotša bontšhi bja oksetšene yeo motho a e hemago," gwa realo molaodiphethiši wa csir future production: manufacturing, elego martin sanne.
tgt: ungakhona kutsi wandzise nome unciphise linani lemoyamphilo umuntfu lawuphefumulako," kusho umlawuli lomkhulu wecsir future production: manufacturing martin sanne.

src: balwetši bao ba šomišago sethušagohema ba se lokelwa maskeng woo ba tla bego ba o apere oksetšene e gogwa go tšwa tankeng ya kgase gomme ya hlakantšhwa le moya wa tlhago ka gare ga sethušagohema, gomme go tloga moo o romelwa maskeng gomme wa hemelwa ka gare ke molwetši.
tgt: tigulane letisebentisa lesisitakuphefumula tichunyaniswa ngekusebentisa sifonyo.

src: sanne o bolela gore godimo ga go pompa moya wa go ba le oksetšene, cpap e thuša gape balwetši gore ba hemele ka ntle.
tgt: umoyamphilo udvonswa ethangeni lelinegesi yemoyamphilo iphindze futsi ibhicaniswe nemoya wemvelo kulesisitakuphefumula, kusuka lapha bese wendluliselwa kulesifonyo bese sigulane siyayihogela.

src: sedirišwa sa cpap se ka šomišwa mafelong a tša maphelo a theknolotši ya godimo gape le ka mafelong a nakwana a bjalo ka maokelo a nakwana le mafelo a boipeelothoko.
tgt: sanne utsi ekwengeteni ekumpompeni umoyamphilo, lecpap iphindze futsi isite tigulane kutsi tiphefumule tikhiphe umoya.

src: sanne a re csir e tla be e kgonne go dira dithušagohema tše 10 000 ge kgwedi ya phato e fihla mafelelong.
tgt: lesisetjentiswa secpap singasetjentiswa kutimondzawo tetekwelapha tebuchwepheshe lobusezingeni lelisetulu nome kutimondzawo tesikhashana, njengasetibhedlela tesikhashana kanye nasetindzaweni tekuhlala wedvwa ngenca yesifo.

src: ka tšhomišano le siemens, simera, akacia, gabler, umoya le yunibesithi ya cape town, csir e tšweleditše cpap go ya le ka melawana ya mokgatlo wa lefase wa tša maphelo.
tgt: sanne utsi icsir itawube seyikhicite tisitakuphefumula leti10 000 ekupheleni kwenyanga yengci.

src: dithušagohema tša mathomo di tla fiwa maokelo a mmušo ao a lego bothateng bja tlhokego ya didirišwa tša go lwantšhana le covid19.
tgt: ngekusebentisana nebakasiemens, simera, akacia, gabler, umoya kanye nenyuvesi yasekapa, icsir ikhicite lecpap ngekulandzela tilinganisozinga tenhlangano yemhlaba yetemphilo.

src: csir e thomile go šomana le cpap morago ga gore lefase le itemogele tlhokego ye kgolo ya dithušagohema.
tgt: tisitakuphefumula tekucala titawunikwa tibhedlela tahulumende leticindzetelekile ngenca yekungabikhona kwetisetjentiswa tekubukana necovid19.

src: thuša go emiša go phatlalala ga covid19 vukuzenzele unnamed setšhaba sa gaborena se lebagane le bothata bjo bogolo historing ya temokrasi ya rena.
tgt: sita kutsi sivimbe kubhebhetseka kwecovid19 vukuzenzele unnamed sive sakitsi sibukene nenkinga lenkhulukati emlandvweni wetfu wentsandvo yelinyenti.

src: mo matšatšing a go feta a 120, re atlegile go diteleng go phatlalala ga baerase yeo e hlolago masetlapelo lefaseng ka bophara.
tgt: ngetulu kwetinsuku leti120, siphumelele kubambelela kubhebhetseka kweligciwane lelibanga umonakalo lomkhulukati emhlabeni wonkhana.

src: efela gabjale go keka ga diphetetšo, fao re kilego ra eletšwa ke ditsebi tša bongaka gore go tlo ba gona, go fihlile.
tgt: kodvwa nyalo, kwandza kakhulu kwekusuleleka leselulekwe ngako tati tetekwelapha kutsi kuyeta, sekufikile.

src: palo ya go feta kotara ya milione ya maafrika borwa e fetetšwe ke coronavirus, gomme ebile re a tseba gore diphetetšo tše dintšhi di iphihlile.
tgt: bangetulu kwekota yesigidzi bantfu baseningizimu afrika lasebasuleleke ngaleligciwane lecorona, siyati futsi kutsi kwesuleleka lokunyenti kusengakabonwa.

src: gabjale go netefatšwa diphetetšo tše diswa tša go feta 12 000 tšatši le lengwe le le lengwe.
tgt: nyalo sesitfola tehlakalo tekwesuleleka letinsha letingetulu kwe12,000 malanga onkhe.

src: esale go tloga mola bolwetši bjo bo phulegago ka kgwedi ya hlakola, go hlokofetše batho ba 4 079 ba bolawa ke covid19.
tgt: kusukela kwacala lokubhedvuka ngenyanga yendlovulenkhulu, lokungenani sekushone bantfu laba4, 079 ngenca yalecovid19.

src: bjalo ka maphoto a magolo a go tonya ao a budulelago ka nageng ya rena go tšwa ka lewatleng la south atlantic mo nakong ye ya ngwaga, go na le dikarolo di se kae tša ka mo nageng tšeo di ka se fihlelelwego ke coronavirus.
tgt: njengaloku kunemakhata lashubisa umnkantja lahlasele lelive lakitsi lachamuka eningizimu yeatlantic ngalesikhatsi semnyaka, timbalwa tincenye talelive letingeke titsintfwe nguleligciwane lecorona.

src: coronaviruse kotsi le go ba šoro kudu go feta efe goba efe yeo e kilego ya ba gona.
tgt: lesivunguvungu saleligciwane lecorona sinelulaka lolukhulu futsi sibhubhisa kakhulu kwengca nome ngabe yini lesikwatiko kwaphambilini.

src: e tloga e tlaralatša mošomo wa didirišwa tša rena le maikemišetšo ka go fetišiša.
tgt: imitfombolusito yetfu isebenta ngalokwecile futsi seyisondzele emikhawulweni yayo.

src: go keka ga diphetetšo, elego seo se akantšwego ke ditsebi le boramahlale ba borena kgweding tše tharo tšeo di fetilego, go fihlile.
tgt: lokwandza kwekwesuleleka tingcweti tetfu tetekwelapha kanye nabososayensi labakubiketele etinyangeni letintsatfu letengcile nyalo sekufikile.

src: go thomile ka kapa bodikela gomme gabjale go tsene ka kapa bohlabela le ka gauteng.
tgt: kucale enshonalanga kapa kantsi futsi sekusendleleni kuya emphumalanga kapa nasegauteng.

src: le ge go le bjalo, ge diphetetšo di golela godimo ka lebelo, go bohlokwa go lemoga gore palo ya mahu ya dipersente tše 1.5 ke ye nngwe ya dipalo tša fasefase lefaseng ge e bapetšwa le ya lefase ya dipersente tše 4.4. go ba fasefase ga palo ya mahu ka nageng ya gaborena go hlotšwe ke maitemogelo le boikgafo bja bašomedi ba tša maphelo gape le magato a tšhoganetšo ao re a tšeerego go hlabolla mokgwa wa tša maphelo.
tgt: nanome kunjalo, ngesikhatsi kusuleleka kwandza kakhulu, kubalulekile kucaphela kutsi lizinga lemaphesenti la1.5 alabo labashonako lisemkhatsini walaphasi kakhulu emhlabeni.

src: mo kgabagareng ya leuba le, go tsena ka gare ga thekisi o se wa apara maske, go kopana le bagwera, go ya meletlong goba gona go etela meloko, go ka phatlalatša baerase gabonolo gomme gwa ba le go lobja ga maphelo.
tgt: lelinani lelincane lalabashonako kulelive kungenca yesipiliyoni kanye nekutinikela kwetingcweti tetfu tetemphilo kanye netinyatselo letiphutfumako lesititsetse sakha emandla ekwenta umsebenti eluhlelweni lwetfu lwetemphilo.

src: bjo e ka no ba e le bolwetši bjoo bo hlolwago ke baerase, efela bo phatlalatšwa ke mekgwa le maitshwaro a batho.
tgt: njengaloku linyenti lebantfu bakitsi batsatse sinyatselo sekuvikela kubhebhetseka kwaleligciwane, kodvwa kukhona labanye labangakwenti loko.

src: re swanetše re apare maske wa lešela woo o khupetšago nko le molomo nako ye nngwe le ye nngwe ge re e tšwa ka gae.
tgt: kusekhona lolubhubhane, kugibela eteksini ungakafaki sifonyo, kuhlangana nebangani, kuhambela imicimbi yemadzili nome ngisho nekuvakashela umndeni, kungabhebhetsekisa leligciwane kalula futsi kube khona labalahlekelwa timphilo tabo.

src: re swanetše re tšwele pele go hlapa diatla ka meetse le sesepe goba sebolayaditwatši ka mehla.
tgt: lesi kungaba sifo lesibangwa ligciwane kodvwa libhebhetsekiswa kutiphatsa kwemuntfu.

src: re swanetše re tšwele pele go hlwekiša le go bolaya ditwatši mabatong ka moka a mafelo a bohle.
tgt: ngenca yetento tetfu – talowo nalowo, temindeni, temimango, – singakhona futsi kufanele kutsi siyigucule indlela yalolubhubhane kulelive lakitsi.

src: sa bohlokwa le go feta ke gore re swanetše re bule sekgoba sa dimitara tše pedi gare ga rena le batho ba bangwe.
tgt: kudzingeka kutsi sifake sifonyo sendvwangu lesivala imphumulo nemlomo nangabe siphuma ekhaya.

src: gabjale go na le bohlatse bjoo bo tšwelelago bja gore baerase ye e ka kgona le go fofa moyeng mo mafelong ao a tletšego batho ba bantšhi, ao a tswalegilego goba ao ka go ona moya o sa sepelego botse.
tgt: kufanele kutsi sichubeke sigeze njalo tandla tetfu ngensipho nemanti nome ngesibulalimagciwane.

src: ka lona lebaka le, re swanetše re hlabolle mafelo a setšhaba ao a tswalegilego ka pelapela, elego fao kotsi ya go fetelwa e lego godimo kudu.
tgt: kufanele kutsi sichubeke sigeze futsi sihlante ngesibulalimagciwane lonkhe lingetulu letindzawo lapho kutfolakala khona bantfu.

src: sephetho sa rena sa go tla ka kiletšo ya mosepelo ya bosetšhaba se thibetše phatlalalo ya diphetetšo mathomong ge ditirelo tša maphelo di be di se tša itokiša, elego seo se ka bego se hlotše tobo ye kgolo ya maphelo.
tgt: lokubaluleke kakhulu, kufanele kutsi sishiye libanga lekukhweshelana leliphephile – lokungenani lemamitha lamabili – kulomunye umuntfu.

src: re šetše re dirile diteko tša coronavirus tša go feta dimilione tše pedi, gomme bašomedi ba tša maphelo ba šetše ba dirile diponego tša go feta dimilione tše 20. re dirile gore go be le mepete e 28 000 ya balwetši ba covid19 ka maokelong, gomme ebile re agile maokelo a nakwana go kgabaganya naga.
tgt: nyalo sekunebufakazi lobusha lobuvelako bekutsi leligciwane lingahlala emoyeni etindzaweni lapho kunesicuku sebantfu, letivalekile nome letingangenisi kahle umoya.

src: gabjale re na le mepete e 37 000 ya boipeelothoko mafelong a poraebete le a setšhaba go kgabaganya naga, gomme a itokišeditše go amogela bao ba sa kgonego go ipeela thoko ka magae.
tgt: ngaleso sizatfuke kufanele kutsi sitente ncono timondzawo letingekhatsi tetindzawo temmango lapho bungoti bekusuleleka ngalesifo bubukhulu kakhulu.

src: re rekile le go aba dimilione tša didirišwa tša go itšhireletša maokelong, dikliniking le dikolong go kgabaganya naga, e lego tša go šireletša bašomedi bao ba šomago ka batho ba bantšhi.
tgt: sincumo setfu sekumemetela kumiswansi kwemisebenti, iminyakato nekuhlala ekhaya kwavelonkhe kwavimbela kusuleleka lokukhulu ekucaleni ngesikhatsi tinsita tetfu tetemphilo betisengakalungeli kahle, lokuyintfo lengabe yaholela ekulahlekelweni kakhulu timphilo tebantfu.

src: re thwetše ebile re sa thwala baoki, dingaka le bašomedi ba tša tšhoganetšo ba tlaleletšo.
tgt: kulesikhatsi lesibe naso, sitsatse tinyatselo letimcoka tekucinisa kuphendvula kwetfu ngekwetemphilo.

src: re tšwela pele go ba le tšwelopele mo maitekelong a rena a go lwantšha covid19, efela tlhotlo ye kgolo e sa etla.
tgt: sesente luhlolo lweligciwane lecorona lolungetulu kwetigidzi letimbili kantsi tisebenti temmango tetemphilo setente luhlolokuhlunga lolungetulu kwetigidzi letinge20.

src: re šoma go kgabaganya diprofense go oketša palo ya mepete ya ka diwateng le ka tlhokomelong yeo e tseneletšego re direla balwetši ba covid19.
tgt: sesente kutsi kube nemibhedze yasesibhedlela yelinani lelifinyelela ku28,000 yetigulane tecovid19 futsi sesakhe netibhedlela tesikhashana letisebentako eveni lonkhe.

src: sekgoba se a bulwa ka maokelong a mmalwa ka go se amogele balwetši bao ba sa hlokego thušo ya tšhoganetšo.
tgt: nyalo sesinemibhedze yekuhlala wedvwa ngenca yesifo lengetulu kwe37,000 kutisetjentiswa letitimele kanye nakutisetjentiswa tahulumende eveni lonkhe, letilungele kwehlukanisa ngayedvwa labo labangakhoni kukwenta nabasemakhaya.

src: go fetolwa gape le mafelo a mangwe ka maokelong go ba diwate tša tlaleletšo, gape le go agwa goba go oketšwa ga maokelo a nakwana.
tgt: sesitsenge saphindza futsi saletsa tisetjentiswa tekutivikela etibhedlela, emitfolamphilo kanye nasetikolweni kulolonkhe lelive kute kutsi sivikele tisebenti tetfu tetemphilo letisembili lapho imphi ishisa khona.

src: re šoma go oketša kabo ya oksetšene, dithušagohema le didirišwa tše dingwe bakeng sa bao ba tlo hlokago tlhokomelo yeo e tseneletšego, go balwa le kabo ya oksetšene bakeng sa mabaka a mangwe.
tgt: siphindze futsi satweba futsi siyachubeka nekutweba bahlengi/bahlengikati labangetiwe, bodokotela kanye netisebenti tetemphilo tesimo lesiphutfumako.

src: re diriša ditheknolotši tša titšithale go matlafatša taetšo, go nyakana gape le go beela thoko balwetši, le go thekga bao diteko tša bona di laetšago ba fetetšwe.
tgt: siyachubeka nekwenta inchubekelembili emitameni yetfu yekubukana nalecovid19, kodvwa insayeya yetfu lenkhulu iseta.

src: bjale ka ge re lebile sehloeng sa diphetetšo, re hloka go ba le tlhokomelo ye kgolo le go thatafatša magato ao a latelwago gabjale go fokotša lebelo la diphetetšo.
tgt: kuto tonkhe tifundza, sisebenta ngemandla kutsi sandzise linani lemawadijikelele kanye nemibhedze yesimo lesibucayi yetigulane te covid19 kutsi ibekhona.

src: melawana ya mabapi le go apara dimaske e tla thatafatšwa.
tgt: umtsamo wemawadi uyandziswa etibhedlela letinengi ngekutsi kubanjelelwe kunakekelwa kwetimo letingaphutfumi, kuguculwa kwaletinye tindzawo etibhedlela kutsi tibe ngemawadi langetiwe kanye nekwakhiwa nekukhuliswa kwetibhedlela tesikhashana.

src: bengmešomo, bengmabenkele le balaodi, baotledi ba dinamelwa tša bohle, gape le balaodi le beng ba meago efe goba efe ya setšhaba, gabjale ba tlamegile semolao go netefatša gore yo mongwe le yo mongwe yoo a tsenago ka moagong goba ka senamelweng sa bona o swanetše go ba a apere maske.
tgt: siyasebenta kute kutsi sandzise kuphakelwa kwemoyamphilo, tisitakuphefumula kanye naletinye tisetjentiswa kulabo labatawudzinga kunakekelwa lokubucayi, lokufaka ekhatsi kujikiswa kuphakelwa kwemoyamphilo kuletinye tinhloso.

src: dithekisi tšeo di tšeago maeto a kgauswi di a dumelelwa go rwala go fihlela dipersenteng tše lekgolo, mola tša maeto a matelele di se tša dumelelwa go feta dipersente tše masomešupa, gomme gona fao go latelwe melawana e meswa ya mabapi le dimaske, go bolaya ditwatši ka dinamelweng gape le go bula mafasetere.
tgt: sisabalalisa tebuchwepheshe bedijithali kute sicinise kubona, kulandzelela kanye nekwehlukanisa kutsi bahlale bodvwa labo labatsintsene nalabesulelekile, kanye nekwesekela labo labahlolwe bakhatfolakala kutsi banaleligciwane.

src: gabjale go na le bohlatse bjoo bo tletšego bja gore thekišo ya dinotagi e hlotše kgatelelo ye kgolo go maokelo, go akaretšwa le ka diyuniting tša maemo a tšhoganetšo le tša tlhokomelo yabao ba bakwago le badimo ka baka la dikotsi tša difatanaga, dikgaruru le mathata a go sepelelana le tšona.
tgt: njengaloku nyalo sesifinyelela ngasezingeni lelisetulu lekusuleleka, sidzinga kutsi sicaphele kakhulu futsi sicinise letinyatselo letikhona kute sehlise lizinga lekundluliseleka kwalesifo.

src: ka fao, re tšeere sephetho sa gore, go re re kgone go lota sekgoba seo se šetšego se le gona ka maokelong, gona thekišo, kabo le phatlalatšo ya dinotagi e tla fegwa go tloga gonabjalebjale.
tgt: tisebenti, banikati betitolo kanye nebaphatsi, labasebentisa tekutfutsa ummango, kanye nebalawuli kanye nebanikati banome ngabe ngusiphi sakhiwo semmango nyalo sebacindzetelwa ngumtsetfo kutsi bacinisekise kutsi nome ngabe ngubani longena emabaleni ato nome logibela sigitjelwa kufanele kutsi afake sifonyo.

src: bjalo ka legato la tlaleletšo la go fokotša tlalelo ya maokelo, ga go na motho yoo a swanetšego go ba ka ntle mebileng go tloga ka iri ya senyane bošego go fihla ka iri ya bone ka masa.
tgt: ematekisi lahamba luhambo lwendzawo avumelekile kutsi alayishe umtsamo wemaphesenti la100 kantsi lawo lahamba emabanga lamadze ngeke avunyelwe kutsi engce umtsamo wemaphesenti lange70, ngaphasi kwesimo sekutsi sendlelanchubo yekunciphisa bungoti lobusha lobuphatselene netifonyo, kufutsa sigitjelwa ngesibulalimagciwane kanye nekuvulwa kwemafasitelo tiyalandzelwa.

src: re tšea magato a re tseba gabotse gore ga a amogelege ebile a bea mapheko maphelong a batho, efela a swanetše gore a tšewe gore re kgone go feta sehloa sa bolwetši.
tgt: nyalo sekukhona bufakazi lobucacile bekutsi kucala futsi kwekutsengiswa kwetjwala kube nemphumela nekucindzeteleka lokukhulu kwetibhedlela, lokufaka ekhatsi emayunithi ekunakekela timo letibucayi tetingoti nemaicu, ngenca yetingoti tetimoto, budlova kanye netingoti letiphatselene naloko.

src: ga go na ka mokgwa woo re ka efogago lephoto la coronavirus, efela re ka kgona go fokotša tshenyo yeo le ka e hlolago maphelong a rena.

src: bjalo ka setšhaba, re a thekgana, re thekga le bao ba lwalago ebile re hlohleletša kamogelo ya batho bao ba phelago ka baerase ye.

src: arendse e be e le yo mongwe wa dialoga tša lenaneo la tlhabollo ya baswa ya chrysalis academy ya mmušo wa kapa bodikela ka 2016. morago ga lenaneo leo, o o ile a šoma setišing sa botimamollo sa ka beaufort west gomme a gola feela r1 900 ka kgwedi.

src: tiragalo ye e dira matswalo a letšatši ka 1956 ge basadi ba 20 000 ba matšhetša union buildings – basadi ba bantši ba go bolela malema a go fapana, go tšwa mafelong a go fapana gomme ba mehlobo ka moka.
tgt: lesikhatsi sekugubha lusuku lwekukhumbula nga1956 ngesikhatsi bomake laba20 000 bashuca baya eunion buildings – sicuku lesikhulu sabomake lebe sikhuluma tilwimi letinengi, labe bavela etindzaweni letahlukene futsi bato tonkhe tinhlanga.

src: ba be ba kopane ka senyakwa sa bona sa go fediša melao ya dipasa le tokelo ya bona ya go phela ka tokologo.
tgt: bebabumbene bayintfo yinye kuloko bebakufuna kutsi kupheliswe imitsetfo lemibi yemapasi kanye nelilungelo labo lekuphila ngenkhululeko.

src: maemo le kemo ya basadi ka afrika borwa lehono a fapana kudu le ao bommago rena le bokoko a rena ba bego ba phela ka fase ga wona ka 1956. re tšwa kgole gore re be le afrika borwa ya go hloka semorafe, ya go hloka kgethologanyo ya bong, ya go huma gape yeo e lokologilego.
tgt: simo sabomake kanye nesikhundla sabo lapha eningizimuafrika lamuhla sesigucuke kakhulu kunaleso bomake betfu kanye nabogogo betfu labebabukene naso nga1956.

src: go bile le tšwelopele kudu mo go kaonafatšeng maphelo a basadi ba afrika borwa go ekonomi, lekala la dipolotiki le go bophelo bja setšhaba.
tgt: sesihambe libanga lelidze ekwenteni iningizimu afrika lengahlukanisi sive ngebuhlanga, ngebulili, yentsandvo yelinyenti, lephumelelako futsi nalekhululekile.

src: go le bjalo, re a tseba gore re sa ya kgole.
tgt: ngalokufananako, siyati kutsi kusasekunengi kakhulu lesingachubeka sikwente.

src: basadi ba sa lebane le kgethollo, tlhorišo le dikgaruru, gomme ba sa phela ka bohloki.
tgt: bomake solo basabukene nekubandlululwa, kugcagcalatiswa nebudlova, futsi ngibo labatsintfwa kakhulu buphuya.

src: ge e le gore ka nnete re nyaka go diragatša tshepišo ya molaotheo wa rena re swanetše go lwantšha dikgato tse di dirago gore basadi ba se be le letseno le tšhelete moo go dirago gore ba ikhwetše ba kgotleletše go hlorišwa le go bethwa.
tgt: nangabe sitawufezekisa ngeliciniso setsembiso semtsetfosisekelo wetfu, kufanele kutsi silungise kukhishelwa ngephandle kutemnotfo kanye nakutetimali kwabomake lokuyintfo leyenta bomake kutsi bahlaseleke lula nabahlukunyetwa kanye nebudlova.

src: re tsenetše lesolo la go ribolla leswika leo le re amantšhago le maitapišo a lefase a go fihlelela tekatekano ya bong ka 2030. tekatekano ya meloko ke agenda ya tlhohleletšo le phetogo go fediša kgethollo le dikgaruru kgahlanong le basadi le bana le go kgatha tema ka go lekana bophelong bja dipolotiki, leago le ekonomi.
tgt: sesijoyine umkhankhaso loyinchophamlandvo losichumanisa nemitamo yemhlaba wonkhe yekufezekisa kulingana ngebulili nga2030.

src: bjalo ka karolo ya lesolo le, re kopantše ‘ditirišano tša twantšho’ tše pedi, yenngwe ke ya toka le ditokelo tša ekonomi ge ye nngwe e le ya kgahlanong le dikgaruru tše di ekadilego ka bong.
tgt: kulingana kwesitukulwane luhlelo lolunekulangatelela kwenta lokukhulu futsi loluguculako lwekucedza kubandlululwa kanye nebudlova lobucondzi swe kubomake kanye nekutimbandzakanya kwabo ngalokulinganako kutepolitiki, kutenhlalo nasemphilweni yetemnotfo.

src: dikgwedi tše 11 go tloga mola leano la twantšho la go arabela la tšhoganetšo go lwantšha dikgaruru tšeo di ikadilego ka bong le dipolao tša basadi (gbvf) ke banna le phethagatšwago go bonagetše tšwelopele go godiša thekgo le tlhokomelo ya bao ba phologilego, gomme go na le tšwelopele go kaonafatšeng molao go ba fa tšhireletšo ye kgolo.
tgt: njengencenye yalomkhankhaso, sijoyine ‘imifelandzawonye’ lemibili , yinye yebulungiswa kutemnotfo nemalungelo kanye lenye ngulemelene nebudlova lobucondziswe kubomake.

src: mo kgweding ya phato, re thoma ka phethagatšo ya leano la peakanyo la bosetšhaba go lwantšha gbvf ke banna.
tgt: totimbili letingcikitsi timcoka vele kuluhlelo lwetfu lwavelonkhe.

src: ntlha ya bohlokwa ya leano le ke go kgonthiša gore basadi ba bantši ba fiwa kudu menyetla mo ditšheleteng.
tgt: tinyanga leti11 kusukela lisu lekwenta kuphendvula simo lesiphutfumako lekulwa nebudlova lobeyamene nebulili kanye nekubulawa kwabomake lafezekiswa sesibe nenchubekelembili ekungeteni kusekela nekunakekela labo labahlukumetekile, futsi kunenchubekelembili leseyentiwe ekuguculeni temtsetfo kutsi bavikeleke kakhulu.

src: maemo a basadi ka afrika borwa a ba dira gore ba be kotsing ya go hlorišwa.
tgt: luhlangotsi lolumcoka kakhulu kulelisu lumayelana nekucinisekisa kufaka kakhulu bomake kutetimali.

src: re swanetše go oketša thekgo ya basadi go ba kgontšha gore ba itirele tšhelete ya bona.
tgt: kufaneleke kutsi senyuse kwesekela kwetfu bomake kute kutsi bakhone kutimela ngekwetetimali.

src: re dirile maikgafo a mmalwa ka fase ga tekatekano ya moloko yeo e tla tšweletšago dipoelo ka leano la peakanyo ya bosetšhaba.
tgt: sesente tetsembiso letinyenti tekutinikela ngaphasi kweluhlelo lwekulingana kwesitukulwane letitawuphumelela ngekusebentisa lisu lavelonkhe lelisubuciko.

src: sa mathomo, re ya go tsentšha basadi mererong ya ekonomi ka go ba abela dithendara.
tgt: kwekucala, sitawuchuba kufakwa kwabomake kutemnotfo ngekutsenga kwahulumende kwenta loko.

src: re beile selebanywa sa go kgonthiša gore bonnyane dithoto le ditirelo tša go lekana 40% tšeo di rekilwego ke makala a setšhaba di tšwe dikgwebong tša basadi.
tgt: sesibeke umgomo wekucinisekisa kutsi lokungenani emaphesenta lange40 etimphahla kanye netinsita letitsengwa tikhungo tahulumende kumabhizinisi banikati bawo kubomake.

src: sa bobedi, re ya go oketša thekgo go dismme tša basadi le go basadi bao ba nago le dikgwebo tša mo mebileng goba bao ba sa šomego.
tgt: kwesibili, sitakwenyusa kwesekelwa kwemasmme laphetfwe bomake kanye nabomake labasebenta emkhakheni longakahleleki nome labo labangasebenti.

src: se se tla akaretša go boledišana le makala a ditšhelete go dira gore ditirelo tša ditšhelete di fihlelelege le go rekega go basadi.
tgt: loku kutawufaka ekhatsi kuhlanganyela nemkhakha wetetimali kute yenta kutsi tinsita tetetimali tifinyelele kubomake futsi tingabiti.

src: sa boraro, re nyaka go kgonthiša gore basadi ba bantši ba na le dithoto tša bohlokwa go swana le naga.
tgt: kwesitsatfu, sifuna kucinisekisa kutsi bomake labanengi bayakhona kufinyelela kutfola timphahla letikhicitako njengemhlaba.

src: go bohlokwa gore basadi e be baholegi ba lenaneo le potlakišitšwego la poelo ya mafase.
tgt: kubalulekile kutsi bomake kuba ngibo labazuzako eluhlelweni lolusheshako lwekugucula temhlaba.

src: go bohlokwa gore go r75 milione ya diboutšhara tšeo di beetšwego kimollo ya covid19 ya kabo ya temo 53% ya baholegi e tla ba basadi ba magaeng.
tgt: kubaluleke kakhulu kutsi kule tigidzi letinger75 tekuhhamula tecovid19 letibekelwe eceleni tekulima, emavawusha emaphesenti lange53 ebazuzi kufanele kutsi kube bomake basetindzaweni tasemaphandleni.

src: re swanetše go kgonthiša gore basadi ba balemi ba ka gae le ba bannyane ba tšwela pele go amogela thekgo ka morago ga leuba.
tgt: kufanele kutsi sicinisekise kutsi balimi lababomake labalimela kutondla kanye nebalimi labancane bayachubeka kutfola kwesekelwa ngisho ngemuva kwalolubhubhane selwendlulile.

src: sa bone, re nyaka go kgonthiša gore basadi ba šireletšwa go dikgaruru tšeo di ikadilego ka bong mo mošomong.
tgt: kwesine, sifuna kucinisekisa kutsi bomake bayavikeleka ebudloveni lobeyame ebulilini etindzaweni tekusebenta.

src: ka tsela yeo re tla ba re šoma legatong la bosetšhaba le la selete go tumelelano ya kopano ya ilo ka ga dikgaruru le tlhorišo mošomong.
tgt: ngaleyo ndlela, sitawube sisebenta ezingeni lavelonkhe kanye neletigodzi ekufeze kiseni sivumelwane somhlangano wenhlangano yetisebenti yemhlaba wonkhe mayelana nebudlova nekugcagcalatiswa etindzaweni tekusebenta.

src: go thwe tokologo ga e fiwe, eupša e a tšewa.
tgt: kutsiwa inkhululeko ayinikwa kodvwa iyatsatfwa.

src: tokologo ya basadi ke mantšu fela ao a lego letlakaleng ntle le ge e ka bapetšwa ke boikgafo go tšwa go makala ka moka a setšhaba.
tgt: kukhululwa kwabomake kunga ba ngemagama nje lasephepheni nangabe akuhambisani nekutinikela kwayo yonkhe imikhakha yemmango.

src: ge re beakanya kagolefsa ya ekonomi ya rena mo tlhohlong ya leuba la coronavirus , re rile re ka se boele moo re bego re le gona pele ga go phulega ga baerase.

src: re swanetše go aga ekonomi ye bohlokwa ya go fapana le yeo re bego re na le yona yeo, gare ga dilo tše dingwe, e kaonafatšago maemo a bohlokwa a basadi.

src: nsfas e phethagatša ditoro tša ka more matshediso setlamo sa setšhaba sa thušo ya ditšhelete tša baithuti (nsfas) se hotše karabo mashego (21) mathateng a gagwe a ditšhelete le go mo thuša go fihlelela leano la gagwe la go tšwetša dithuto tša gagwe pele.
tgt: insfas yaphumelelisa emaphupho ami more matshediso sikimu savelonkhe sekusita titjudeni ngetimali (nsfas) sivale leligeba letimali emkhatsini kwa karabo mashego (21) naseluhlelweni lwakhe lwekuchubeka ngetifu ndvo takhe.

src: mashego wa go tšwa sebo keng profenseng ya gauteng tikologong ya vaal o bolela gore a ka be a sa kgona go fihlelela ditefo tša dithuto tša gagwe le disenyegelo tše dingwe tša go tsamaišana le dithuto tša ka morago ga marematlou ge nkabe a sa hwetša pasari go tšwa nsfas.
tgt: mashego wasesebokeng egauteng endzaweni yasevaal utsi bekangeke akhone kukhokhela imali yekufundza naletinye ti ndleko letita nekuchubeka kufundza emva kweku photfula matikuletjeni uma bekangakatfoli umfundzate lobuya kunsfas.

src: "godimo ga mo, tšhelete ya kgwedi ka kgwedi yeo ke e hwetšago go tšwa nsfas e nkgontšha gore ke ithute le gore ke se robale ka tlala," a realo.
tgt: "kwengeta, imali lengiyi tfola njalo ngenyanga levela kunsfas ingenta ngi khone kulala futsi ngi fundze ngisutsi," usho njalo.

src: mashego ke moithuti wa ngwaga wa boraro dithutong tša gagwe tša lengwalo la degree ya civil engineering kua yunibesithing ya pretoria.
tgt: mashego ungumfundzi lowenta umnyaka wesitsa tfu kutifundvo tebunjiniye la enyunivesi yasepretoria.

src: "ditefelo tša thuto di tura ka maatla.
tgt: "tindleko tekufundza tibi ta kakhulu.

src: ka dithuto tšeo ke di kgethilego, nkabe ke saka ka kgona go lefela dikgwedi tše tshela, ke sa bolele ka ngwaga o tee wa dithuto," a hlaloša mashego.
tgt: kuletifundvo lengitikhetsile, ecinisweni bengingeke ngikhone kukhokhela tinyanga letisitfupha, angisakhulumi ngemnyaka wekufundza lowodvwa," uyachaza.

src: mashego o feditše mare matlou ka 2016 e le moithuti wa go šoma bokaonekaone ka mphatong wa gagwe, eupša o be a hloka tšhelete ya go lefela dithuto tša gagwe.
tgt: mashego watfola mati kuletjeni ngemnyaka we2016 futsi bekamfundzi lowaphuma embili eklasini lakhe, kodvwa angenayo indlela yekukhokhela tifundvo takhe.

src: o ile a atlega dikgopelong tša gagwe tša thekgo ya tšhelete go tšwa nsfas ka ngwaga wa dithuto wa 2018.
tgt: sicelo sakhe selusito lwetimali kunsfas saphumelela ngemnyaka wekufundza we2018.

src: "se se mphile monyetla wa go dira toro yaka ya go ithutela engineering go ba nnete.
tgt: "loku kwanginika litfuba lekuphumelelisa liphupho lami lekufundzela bunji niyela.

src: thuto e kgatha tema ye bohlokwa kudu tlhabo llong yaka ebile e nthuša go gatela pele go tšeo ke ikemišeditšego go di fihlele la.
tgt: imfundvo idlala indzima lenkhulu ekuti tfutfukiseni futsi iyangisita kutsi ngichubekele embili kuko konkhe bengifisa ku phumelela kuko.

src: go feta mo, e mmatlafatša gore ke maatlafatše batho ba bangwe setšhabeng sa gešo ka gona ke kgathe tema tlhabollong ya ikonomi ya naga ya gaborena," gwa hlaloša mashego.
tgt: ngetulu kwaloko, inginika emandla ekutfutfukisa labanye ba ntfu emmangweni wanga kitsi ngaloko ifaka ligalelo kumnotfo walelive letfu," kuchaza mashego.

src: "ke hlohleletša baswa go dira dikgopelo tša thekgo ya tšhelete tša nsfas ka gobane go latela toro ya gagwe ga se mahala, go nyakega thekgo ya tšhelete, ebile nsfas e tla go tšwela mohola," a realo.
tgt: "ngincusa bantfu labasha kutsi bafake ticelo telusito lwetimali kunsfas ngoba kuphumelelisa liphupho lakho akuchamuki ma hhala, kudzinga lusito lwetimali, kantsi insfas itakuvalela lelo geba," usho njalo.

src: tona ya thuto ya godimo, saense le diphetogo, ngaka blade nzimande, o butše dikgopelo tša nsfas tša 2021, go tloga ka la 3 phato go fihla ka la 30 dibatsela 2020. baithuti ba go tšwa mae mong ao ba gotšego ka go sokola le bao ba šomago eupša ba rata go tšwetša dithuto tša bona pele ditlha hlong dife goba dife tša mmušo, tša sethekniki le tša thutatiro (tvet), kholetšeng goba yunibesithing, ba ka dira dikgopelo.
tgt: indvuna yetemfundvo lephakeme,yetesayensi neyetekucanjwa kwaloku sha, dkt.

src: gore o kgone go dira kgope lo ya nsfas, modirakgopelo o swanetše go ba modudi wa afrika borwa a be a tšwe lape ng leo mogolo wa lona ge o kopane wa ngwaga ka moka o se fete r350 000. mogolo wo kopanego wa lapa wa ngwaga ka moka go baithuti bao ba nago le bogole ga wa swanela go feta r600 000.
tgt: blade nzimande, sevele uvule sikhatsi lesitinyanga letine temjikeleto wemnyaka we2021 weku faka ticelo kunsfas, ku suka mhla ti3 ingci kuya kumhla ti30 lweti 2020. titjudeni lebetincishwe ematfuba phambilini naleteswele letifisa ku chubeka netifundvo tato kunoma nguliphi likolishi lahulumende letethekhni khi neletemakhono kute mfundvo netekuceceshwa (tvet) noma enyunivesi tingafaka ticelo.

src: "mo ngwageng wo wa ditšhelete, nsfas e thekgi le baithuti ba go feta 700 000, ba 248 242 ba dikholetšeng tša tvet le ba 481 339 ba diyunibesithing (baithuti ka tshedimošo ya boingwadišo).
tgt: kute ukhone kutfola kusekelwa ngetimali yinsfas, lofaka sicelo kufuneka abe sakhamuti saseningizimu afrika futsi abe aphuma emnde nini lonelinani lemholo seli hlangene lonkhe lemnya ka lelingengci r350 000. lemali leholwa ngumndeni ngemnyaka yetitjudeni letinekukhubateka akufu neki ibe ngetulu kwer600 000.

src: nsfas e arabela 40% ya palo ya baithuti bao ba sa ithutela mangwalo a bona a mathomo diyunibesithing le 70% ya dikholetšeng tša tvet.
tgt: "kulomnyaka lona weku fundza, insfas isekele ngetimali titjudeni letinge tulu kwe700 000, leti248 242 letisemakolishi etvet naleti481 339 letisema nyunivesi (titjudeni letikho mbisa kutsi setibhalisiwe).

src: vka fao o ka dirago dikgopelo badiradikgopelo ba swanetše go etela www.
tgt: vindlela longafaka ngayo sicelo labafaka sicelo kufuneka bavakashele www.

src: nsfas.
tgt: nsfas.

src: org.
tgt: org.

src: za ke moka ba kgotle mo go mynsfas .
tgt: z a bese bachafata kumynsfas .

src: ba swanetše go itirela akhaonto ya nsfas, ba kgotle mo go apply, ba arabe dipotšišo tšeo di tšwelelago skrining le go lokela dito kumente tšeo di nyakegago fao.
tgt: kufuneka bativulele iakhawunti yemynsfas , chafata inki nobho letsi apply, phendvula imibuto lekusikrini bese ufaka emadokhumenti ladzingekako.

src: ge ba feditše, ba swanetše go kgotla mo go submit .
tgt: uma loku sebakwentile, kufuneka bachafate submit .

src: morago ga ge ba kgotlile submit, no moro ya referense ya kgopelo yeo e tla tšwelela mo skrining.
tgt: emva kwekuchafata submit , ino mbolo leyireferensi yesicelo sakho itawuvela kusikrini.

src: nomoro yeo ya re ferense e tla romelwa gape mo nomorong ya sellathekeng le atereseng ya imeile yeo modirakgopelo a fanego ka yona.
tgt: lenombolo leyirefe rensi itawuphindza itfunyelwe kunombo lo yamakhalekhikhini wakho nakulikheli leimeyili leliniketwe ngilofaka sicelo.

src: badirakgopelo ba ka šomiša sellathe keng, theipolete goba khomphuthara go dira kgopelo.
tgt: labafaka sicelo bangasebentisa makhalekhikhini, ithebulethi noma ikho mpiyutha kufaka sicelo.

src: phothale ya nsfas e nale diphetogo tša go se iše kae go dira gore go be bonolo go e šomiša le gore e bolokege kudu.
tgt: iphothali yensfas ibe netingucuko letincane le tenta kutsi kube malula kuyisebentisa netekukhulisa kuvikeleka.

src: go badiradikgopelo ba mathomo go nyakega khophi ya bona ya pasa goba sethifikeithi sa matswalo ebile ba swanetše go itirela profaele phothaleng ya nsfas.
tgt: labafaka sicelo kwekucala kufuneka babe nekhophi yeid noma yesitifiketi sekutalwa kute babhalise bese batakhela iphrofayili kuphothali yamynsfas .

src: badiradikgopelo bao ba dirago dikgopelo lekga la bobedi ba swanetše go tsena diakhantong tša bona – gopola, go dumeletšwe fela profaele ye tee ka modirakgopelo.
tgt: labafaka sicelo lesevele baneakhawunti kufuneka bangene kuakhawunti yabo – khumbula, kuvumeleke iphrofayili leyo dvwa kuphela kuloyo lofaka sicelo.

src: modirakgopelo o swanetše go fana ka tumelelo ya gore tshedimošo ka ga yena e lekolwe ke lekoko la boraro ebile ge a ka se dumele se, a ka se dumelelwe go tšwelapele ka tshepedišo ya kgopelo.
tgt: labafaka sicelo kufuneka bavume kutsi lwatiso lolumayelana nabo luhlolwe ngu muntfu wesitsatfu kodvwa uma banga vumelani naloku, angeke bavunyelwe kuchubeka nenchubo yekufaka sicelo.

src: ka baka la leuba la coronavirus , go ka se nyakege gore badiradikgopelo ba romele goba ba lokele foromo ya tumelelano.
tgt: ngenca yalobhubhane weligciwane lecorona, labafaka sicelo angeke kudzi ngeke kutsi batfumele noma bafake lifomu lekunika imvumo.

src: legatong la yona, ba tlo kgopelwa gore ba amogele dipeelano tše lego mo foromong ya tumelelano ya gona fao kgopelong, gotee le melawana le dipeelano tša thekgo ya tšhelete.
tgt: kunaloko, batawucelwa kutsi bavume imibandzela lekulifomu lekuvuma lelielekhthronikhi, lelihambisana nemigomo nemibandzela yekutfola lusito lwetimali.

src: šireletšang basadi le bana ba rena vukuzenzele unnamed ngwaga wo o feti lego, go nyaka go fihla lehono, diketekete tša basadi, tša banna le bana ba ile ba gwantela palamenteng go tliša ditšhupetšo kgahlanong le bothata bja go katwa le go bolawa ga basadi le bana.
tgt: vikela bomake nebantfwana betfu vukuzenzele unnamed kulomnyaka lo phelile, cishe ngulelilanga leli, tinkhulungwane tabomake, bobabe nebantfwana bashuca balibangisa ephalamende bayokhala ngekubhebhetseka kwekudlwengula nekubulawa kwabomake nebantfwana.

src: ka nako yeo, setšhaba se be se sa tšhošitšwe ke go bolawa ga uyinene mrwetyana, leighandre jegels, jesse hess le ga basadi ba bangwe ba bantši bao ba lahlegetšwego ke maphelo a bona ka diatleng tša banna ba bašoro.
tgt: ngaleso sikhatsi, sive besisebu hlungwini lobukhulu bekubulawa kukauyinene mrwetyana, leighandre jegels, jesse hess kanye nalabanye bomake labanyenti laba lahlekelwa timphilo tabo etandleni temadvodza lanesibhuku.

src: go tšwa maemong a bona a go fapana, bafsa le batho ba bagolo, baithuti le basadi bao ba šomago, bagwanti bao ba bego ba dira ditšhupetšo ka khutšo ba be ba emišeditše godimo dipolakate tšeo di bego di ngwadilwe ‘enough is enough’ le ‘am i next?
tgt: kuyo yonkhe imikhakha yetenhlalo, labadzala nalabancane, titjudeni nabomake labasebentako, lababhikishi labebashuca ngekuthula bebaphetse tigwabhugwabhu lebetibhalwe kutsi 'enough is enough ' futsi ' am i next?'

src: bohloko le go befelwa ga bagwanti bao bo be bo le nyanyeng ka letšatši leo.
tgt: buhlungu nentfukutselo lejulile ngalelo langa.

src: ge ke amogela dinyakwa tša bona tšeo di bego di hlagišitšwe ka fao go kwagala ka gona, go bile nyanyeng go nna gore re swanetše go dira se sengwe ka tšhoganetšo le ka maikemišetšo.
tgt: ngesikhatsi ngemukela tidzingo tabo lebebatifuna nge mandla lebetibekwe ngalokucacile, kwangikhanyela kutsi sidzinga kutsa tsa tinyatselo ngalokuphutfumako nangekutimisela.

src: go bile bohlokwa go nna gore ke se ke ka fetola dinyakwa tše ka mantšu a go se kwagale le ka ditshepišo tšeo re ka se di phethagatšego.
tgt: kimi bekubalulekile kutsi ngingaphendvulinje ngemagama lalula netitsembiso letingenalutfo.

src: matšatši a mmalwa ka morago ga fao, ke ile ka bitša tulo ya mohlakanelwa ya palamente, fao re tsebišitšego leanotiro la phetolo ya tšhoganetšo la r1.6 pilione ka nepo ya go lwantšha dikgaruru tša bong le polao ya basadi (gbvf).
tgt: ngemuva kwemalanga lambalwa, ngabita umhlangano wetindlu tephalamende totimbili, lapho khona samemetela lisutinyatselo lekuphendvula ngekuphutfuma letigidzigidzi letir1.6 lekulwa nebudlova lobucondziswe kubulili lobutsite kanye nekubulawa kwalabasikati (igbvf).

src: mo dikgweding tše tshela tša go tsenya tirišong ga leanotiro le, go šomiša ditšhelete tša setšhaba ka dikgorong tša mehutahuta tša mmušo go ile gwa bewa pele ka leswa ka nepo ya go tsekga ditsenogare tša tlhokomelo le thekgo ya batšwasehlabelo, go masolo a temošo le a thibelo ya dikgaruru tše, go kaonafatša melao le melaotshepetšo, go tšwetša pele maatlafatšo ya basadi ka ekonoming, le go maatlafatša tshepedišo ya toka go bosenyi.
tgt: kuletinyanga letisitfupha tekufezekisa, kusetjentiswa kwemali yahulu mende ematikweni ahulumende la manyenti kwabekwa embili kute kutsi kwesekelwe tingenelelo tekunakekela kanye nekwesekelwa kwalabasindzile labanyenti, kwesekelwe imikhankhaso yekucaphelisa nekuvikela, kwenta kancono imitsetfo netinchubomgomo, kukhutsata kuhlonyiswa kwabomake ngetemnotfo, kanye nekucinisa inchubo yetebulungiswa betebugebengu.

src: gomme mo lebakeng le re mo mafelelong a go hlama melao ye bohlokwa leswa ka nepo ya go lwantšha gbvf.
tgt: manje sisezingeni lekulungisa kushaywa kwemtsetfo lokutawuba nelifutse lelikhulu ekulweni negbvf .

src: melaokakanywa ye meraro ye bohlokwa ya go amana le dikgaruru tša bong (gbv) e tsebagaditšwe ka palamenteng mo nakong ye e sa tšwago go feta.
tgt: kusandza kwetfulwa ephalamende imitsetfosivivinyo lemitsatfu lemikhulu lephatselene negbvf .

src: ka go tsebagatša melaokakanywa ye, re hlompha tshepišo yeo re e dirilego go bagwanti ngwageng wo o fetilego le go basadi ba naga ye ka moka.
tgt: ngekunge niswa kwalemitsetfosivivinyo, sigcina sitsembiso lesasenta kubabhikishi kulomnyaka lophelile nakubo bonkhe bomake balelive.

src: melaokakanywaphetošwa ye meraro ye e hlametšwe go tloša sekgoba seo se dumelelago gore basenyi ba melato ye ba tšhabele toka le go phethagatša ka botlalo ditokelo tša basadi le bana ba naga ye.
tgt: lemitsetfosivivinyo yekuchibela lemitsatfu yentelwe kugcwalisa tikhala letivumela babhebhetseli balobuge bengu kutsi bagweme bulungiswa kanye nekwenta kutsi emalungelo abomake nebantfwana balelive kutsi asebente ngalokuphelele.

src: melaokakanywa ye, ge e šetše e phethilwe, e tla thuša go bušetša sekeng tshepo ya basadi ba naga ya rena ya gore molao o gona go ba šireletša.
tgt: lemitsetfosivivinyo, uma seyi photfuliwe, itawusita kubuyisa kutetsemba kwabomake balelive lakitsi kutsi umtsetfo ukhona ngempela kutewubavikela.

src: wa mathomo ke molaokakanywa wa go fetoša molaophetošwa wa bosenyi (wa melato ya thobalano le ye e amanago le ona).
tgt: lomtsetfosivivinyo wekucala uchibela umtsetfo wetebugebengu (emacala wetemacansi netindzaba letiphatselene nawo) umtsetfo wekuchibela.

src: se se dira gore tšhošetšo ka tša thobalano e be molato o moswa, o katološa mollwane wa molato wa go robalana le wa leloko, ebile o katološa maikarabelo a go bega melato ga batho bao ba belaelago gore go dirilwe molato wa thobalano wo o dirilwego kgahlanong le ngwana.
tgt: loku kwenta licala lelisha lekwesabisa ngetemacansi, ukhu lisa bubanti belicala lebundlundlulu, uphindze futsi ukhulisa umsebenti wekubika webantfu labasola kutsi kukhona licala letemacansi lelentiwe kumntfwana.

src: o oketša mollwane wa retšistara ya bosetšhaba ya basenyi ba tša thobalano (nrso) gore e akaretše le dintlha tša basenyi ka moka ba tša thobalano.
tgt: ukhulisa bubanti berejista yavenkhe yetigilamkhuba tetemacansi (inrso) kutsi ifake ekhatsi imininingwane yetigilamkhuba tetemacansi.

src: go fihla mo lebakeng le, e be e dirišwa fela go basenyi ba tša thobalano bao ba bonwego molato wa bosenyi bja thobalano bjo bo dirilwego kgahlanong le bana goba kgahlanong le batho bao ba nago le bofokodi bja ka menaganong.
tgt: kute kube ngumanje, beyiloku isebenta kutigilamkhuba tetemacansi letilahlwe ngemacala ebugebengu betemacansi labhebhetselwa kubantfwana noma bantfu labangaphili kahle engcondvweni.

src: nako yeo dintlha tša mosenyi di swanetšego go ba ka retšistareng e okeditšwe, gomme bao ba ngwadilwego ka gare ga retšistara ba tla swanela go tsebagatša se ge ba romela dikgopelo tša mošomo go ya go šoma le batho bao ba lego kotsing.
tgt: sikhatsi imininingwane yesigilamkhuba letawusihlala kurejista sikhulisiwe, futsi labo lababhalwe kulerejista batawudzingeka kutsi bakudzalule loku uma bafaka ticelo tabo temisebenti tekusebenta nebantfu labahlaseleka kalula.

src: molaokakanywa wo o hlagiša gore maina a batho bao ba lego ka nrso a hwetšagale setšhabeng.
tgt: lomtsetfosivivinyo uphindze ubeke kutsi emagama ebantfu labakunrso afanele kutsi atfolwe sive.

src: molaokakanywaphetošwa wa bosenyi le melato ye e amanago le ona o tiiša, gareng ga tše dingwe, go fa peila go basenyi ba gbvf, ebile o oketša kotlo ya melato yeo gomme go na le lebakanako la fasana leo le beilwego la gore motho yo a bonwe go molato a romelwe kgolegong.
tgt: lomtsetfosivivinyo wekuchibela tebugebengu netindzaba letiphatselene naloko ucinisa, emkhatsini waletinye tintfo, kunikwa ibheyili kwebabhebhetseli begbvf , uphindze futsi wengete emacala lafanele kutsi ahlisisebetwe tigwebo letincane.

src: diphetošo tše di tliša ditlamego tše diswa go bahlankedi ba phethagatšo ya molao le go dikgorotsheko tša rena.
tgt: letichibelo tihlisibeta tibopho letisha kutikhulu tekucinisekisa kugcinwa kwemtsetfo nasetinkantolo tetfu.

src: ge mosekiši a sa ganane le peila mabakeng a gbv , o swanetše go ngwala mabaka a bona.
tgt: uma umshushisi angayiphikisi ibheyili emacaleni egbv , bafanele kutsi babhale kumarekhodi tizatfu tabo.

src: ka ntle le ge motho yo a pharwago ka molato wa dikgaruru tša bong a ka fa mabaka ao a sego a tlwaelega gore ke ka lebaka la eng a swanetše go lokollwa ka peila, kgorotsheko e swanetše go laela gore a golegwe go fihla ge ditshepedišo tša bosenyi di phethwa.
tgt: ngaphandle uma ngabe umuntfu losolwa kutsi wente licala legbv anganiketa timo letikhetseke kakhulu tekutsi kungani bafanele kutsi bakhululwe ngebheyili, inkantolo ifanele kutsi yente bavalelwe kute kube ngulapho sekuphotfulwe tinchubo tetebugebengu.

src: ge di fihlelela sephetho ka ga kgopelo ya peila, dikgorotsheko di gapeletšega go hlokomela dilo tše mmalwa.
tgt: ekufinyeleleni tincumo nekufaka sicelo sebheyili, tinkantolo ticindzeteleka kutsi tibuke tintfo letinyenti.

src: di akaretša dipego tša pele ga tsheko ka ga go nyakega ga go lokolla mopharwakamolato ka peila, ka ga ditšhošetšo tša dikgaruru tše di dirilwego kgahlanong le motšwasehlabelo, lemaikutlo a motšwasehlabelomabapi le polokego ya gagwe.
tgt: tifaka ekhatsi imibiko yangembi kwekutekwa kwelicala lemayelana nekufuna kukhululwa kwemsolwa ngebheyili, kwesatjiswa ngebudlova lokwentiwe kulosindzile, kanye nembono waloyo losindzile mayelana nekuphepha kwakhe.

src: ge re etla go parola, mongongoregi goba wa leloko la motšwasehlabelo yo a hlokofetšego o swanetše go tliša tlhagišo go lekgotla la diparola.
tgt: mayelana neludzaba lepharoli,ummangali noma sihlobo semufi sifanele kutsi sikwati kwetfula inkhulumo ebhodini yepharoli, uma kubukwa lamazinga lasetulu ngalokungemukeleki ebudlova bebalingani betitsandzani kulelive lakitsi, sesicinise imigomo yemtsetfo webudlova basekhaya.

src: ka lebaka la maemo a go se amogelege a dikgaruru tša baratani ka mo nageng ya rena, re tiišitše ditlhagišo tša molao wa dikgaruru tša ka malapeng.
tgt: manje budlova buchazwa ngendlela yekutsi bufaka ekhatsi kukhulumisana, kujola, kubudlelwane besintfu, kwenta mbamba letiphatselene nemacansi noma kutilingisa, budlelwane betemacansi noma budlelwane betemacansi banoma sikhatsi lesingakanani.

src: dikgaruru tša ka malapeng bjale di hlalošwa bjalo ka tšeo di akaretšago le tša bao ba tshephišanego lenyalo, baratani, bao ba lego ka maratong a setšo, le dikamano tšeo di bonwago e le tša marato, tša thobalano goba tša bong tšeo di ka tšeago lebaka lefe goba lefe.
tgt: lomtsetfosivivinyo uphindze futsi welule inchazelo 'yebudlova basekhaya' kutsi ifake ekhatsi kuvikelwa kwebantfu labadzala ekutsini bangahlukunyetwa ngemalunga emndeni.

src: molaokakanywa wo o katološa tlhalošo ya ‘dikgaruru tša ka malapeng’ go akaretša tšhireletšo ya batšofadi kgahlanong le tlaišo ka maloko a lapa.
tgt: bamangali batawukwati kufaka sicelo semyalo wenkantolo wekuvikeleka ngekusebentisa tebucwepheshe.

src: bangongoregi ba tla kgona go dira kgopelo ya taelo ya tšhireletšo ba šomiša inthanete.
tgt: kuvikela simo lapho khona babh ebhetseli bangabhaca ngemuva kwemilandvo yesikhatsi lesendlulile yebudlova basekhaya, kutawusungulwa silondvoloti lesihlanganisile semiyalo yekuvikeleka.

src: go thibela seemo seo go sona basenyi ba ka utago histori ya bona ye e fetilego ya dikgaruru tša ka malapeng tšeo ba di dirilego, lenaneo leo le ikemego leo le kopantšwego la ditaelo tša tšhireletšo le tla hlongwa.
tgt: letichibelo letiphakanyisiwe tiphindze futsi tetfwese litiko letekutfutfukiswa kwetenhlalo, temfundvo lesisekelo, temfundvo lephakeme netemphilo sibopho sekunika labo labasindzile tinsita letitsite nekubendlulisela etindzaweni tekukhosela nekunakekelwa ngetekwelashwa.

src: diphetošo tše di šišintšwego di gapeletša gape kgoro ya tlhabollo ya leago, kgoro ya thuto ya motheo, kgoro ya thuto ya godingwana le kgoro ya maphelo go fana ka ditirelo tše itšego go batšwasehlabelo fao go hlokagalago le go ba romela madulong a itšego le go hwetša tlhokomelo ya kalafo.
tgt: timo lapho khona umshushisi angala kushushisa uma kwentiwe emacala ngaphansi kwalomtsetfo lochitjelwe noma esule tinhlawulo uma ngabe kufaka ekhatsi kulinyatwa umtimba noma uma ngabe kwasetjentiswa silimato kwesabisa ummangali kunemkhawulo.

src: mabaka ao ka ona mosekiši a ka ganago go sekiša ge go dirilwe melato ka fase ga molao wo o fetošitšwego goba go gomiša dipharo ka molato tše di amanago le go kweša motho bohloko mmeleng goba fao e lego gore go šomišitšwe sebetša go tšhošetša mongongoregi di diretšwe mellwane.
tgt: mhlawumbe kusichibelo lesiphakanyisiwe lesiyincophamlandvo kulomtsetfo, uma ngabe kunemuntfu lonelwati, kukholelwa lokwenele noma tinsolo tekutsi kukhona sento sebudlova basekhaya lesentiwe kumntfwana, umuntfu lonekukhubateka noma umuntfu lomdzala futsi ehluleke kubikela sonhlalakahle noma liphoyisa bangahlawuliswa noma baboshwe.

src: mohlomongwe phetošo ye bohlokwa kudu go molao wo, ke ge motho a tseba, a dumela ka fao go kwagalago goba a belaela gore go na le tiro ya dikgaruru tša ka malapeng ye e dirilwego kgahlanong le ngwana, kgahlanong le mogolofadi goba kgahlanong le motšofadi gomme a palelwa ke go bega tiragalo yeo go modirelaleago goba go tirelo ya maphodisa ya afrika borwa (saps) motho yoo a ka faenwa goba aromelwa kgolegong.
tgt: ngalokufananako, kwehluleka kwelilunga lesaps kuhambisana netibopho tabo ngaphansi kwemtsetfo kutawutsatfwa njengekungatiphatsi kahle futsi ufanele kutsi abikwe kubomabhalane betemisebenti yemaphoyisa.

src: woza matrics e tsebagaditšwe dale hes lenaneo la woza matrics le ikemišeditše go thuša baithuti ka moka ba kreiti ya 12 go atlega ditlhahlobong tša bona tša mafelelong a ngwaga.

src: baithuti ba mare matlou ba ngwa ga wo ba tla leba na le mathata a magolo ka lebaka la coronavirus (covid19).

src: kgoro ya thuto ya motheo e netefaditše gore go bulwa ga dikolo ka fao go bolokegilego ke ye nngwe ya dilo tšeo e di beilego pele, gotee le go thekga baithuti ka mananeo a mehutahuta go ba thuša gore ba phete ngwaga wa bona wa dithuto ka katlego.
tgt: litiko letemfundvo lesise kelo lente sicinisekiso sekutsi kubuye kuvulwe kwetikolwa futsi ngalokuphephile kungulokunye kwetintfo tabo letingubomacalangaye, kanye nekusita bafundzi ngetinhlelo letehlukene kubasita baphotfule ngemphumelelo umnyaka wabo wekufundza.

src: ye nngwe ya tše ke lenaneo la woza matrics , leo le tsebagaditšwego semmušo ka la 1 lewedi ka tirišano le badirišanimmogo ba mmalwa ba kgašo le ditsebi tša thuto.
tgt: kunye kwaloku luhlelo lwewoza matrics , lolwetfulwa mhla lu1 inyoni ngekubambisana nebalingani betekusakata labanyenti kanye netingcweti kutemfundvo.

src: bjalo ka karolo ya lenaneo le, dithutwana tša tlaleletšo ka ga dithuto tše bohlokwa tše tshela tša marematlou di gašwa go sabc, dstv le go openview (channel 122) letšatši le lengwe le le lengwe mo dibekeng tše 12, go thoma ka iri ya seswai mesong go fihla ka iri ya lesome mesong le ka iri ya pele mosegare go fihla ka iri ya boraro mathapama.
tgt: njengencenye yaloluhlelo, kusakatwa emoyeni tifundvo tekubamba sikhatsi lesilahlekile letibalulekile letisitfupha kusabc, dstv nakuopen view (ishaneli122) onkhe malanga emaviki la12, kusukela ngensimbi ye8 ekuseni kuye ensimbini ye10 ekuseni nangensimbi ye1 emini kuye ensimbini ye3 emini.

src: woza matrics e lemoga gore le ge baithuti ka moka ba lahlegetšwe ke nako ya sekolo, baithuti ba kreiti ya 12 ke bona bao ba amegilego gampe kudu, ka ge meputso ya bona e le bohlokwa kudukudu gore ba hwetše mešomo le go amogelwa ka diyunibesithing.
tgt: iwoza matrics iyakubona kutsi ngesikhatsi lapho khona bonkhe bafundzi balahlekelwe sikhatsi sesikolwa, kepha belibanga le12 batsintseke kakhulu, ngobe emamaki abo abaluleke kakhulu mayelana nemisebenti yabo kanye nekwemukelwa emanyuvesi.

src: tona ya kgoro ya thuto ya motheo angie motshekga o bolela gore lenaneo le le bohlokwa, ka lebaka la ge go ithuta go šitišitšwe ka lebaka la covid19 .

tgt: gov.

src: bobegaditaba bja afrika borwa ke kokwane ye bohlokwa ya temokrasi ya rena vukuzenzele unnamed mo dinageng tše dintši go pha tlalala le lefase, leuba la coronavirus le diri le gore go be le kiletšo ya ditokologo tša badudi tše dintši gomme la šikinya kopano ya leago.
tgt: tetindzaba taseningizimu afrika tiyinsika lebalulekile yentsandvo yelinyenti yetfu vukuzenzele unnamed emaveni lamanyenti emhlabeni jikelele, lubhubhane lwecorona lubite kutsi kuncishi swe tinkhululeko tebantfu letinyenti lwaphindze futsi lwavivinya telubumbano lwetenhlalo.

src: eupša dinaga tšeo di nago le diinstitušene tše maatla, mananeo a molao a go ela maemo hloko le bobegadi taba bjo maatla di dutše di kgona go thibela go nyatšwa ga ditokelo tša batho le gore taolo ya mmušo e se šomišwe bošaedi.
tgt: kepha emave lanetikhungo letinemandla, tinchubo tete bulungiswa letihlala tica phele kanye nebetindzaba labanemandla akhonile ku vikela emalungelo ebantfu ekutsini anganyatselwa ku phindze futsi kusetjentiswe kabi ligunyamandla lembuso.

src: e šetše e le dikgwedi tše tshela mola go tsebišwago maemo a bosetšhaba a ma setlapelo.
tgt: setinyanga letisitfupha solo kwamenyetelwa inhlekelele yavelonkhe.

src: ntle le mokgwa wa moswananoši wa bolwetši le tlhohlo ye kgolo ya go bea naga ya batho ba 58 milione ka fase ga go dula ka gae, re šomile gabotse.
tgt: nanomanje lesimo salesifo kanye ne tinsayeya taso letijule kabi letente lelive lelinebantfu labatigidzi letinge58 kutsi babe ngaphansi kweku valelwa lokukhulu, sichube kahle kakhulu.

src: re kgonne go laola go phatlalala ga bolwetši kudu ka lebaka la tirišano le tlhokomelo ya badudi.
tgt: sikhonile kulawula kubhebhetseka kwalesifo ikakhulu ngenca yekubambisana nekucaphela kwato tonkhe takhamiti.

src: se se kgonagetše ka lebaka la mošomo wo mobotse wa bobegaditaba bja rena.
tgt: loku kwentiwe kakhulu ngumsebenti lobabatakekako webetindzaba.

src: re swanetše go leboga boraditaba/mmaditaba ba go šoma ka maatla gape ba maikemišetšo ba afrika bo rwa.
tgt: siswele imilomo letinkhu lungwane yekubonga tintsa tseli talapha eningizimu afrika ngekusebenta nge kutikhandla kwato.

src: ba thušitše go abela badudi ba rena tshedimošo ka go phatlalatša melaetša ya maphelo ka ga go se batamelane kudu le go hlweka.
tgt: bagcine bantfu bakitsi batfola lwatiso ngekubendlulisela imila yeto yetemphilo lebalulekile mayelana nekukhweshelana kanye nekuhlanteka.

src: ba dirile se ka fase ga maemo a boima, gantši ka methopo yeo e se ya lekanago.
tgt: bente loku ngaphansi kwetimo letimatima kakhulu, futsi imvamisa basebentisa imi tfombolusito lenemikhawulo.

src: ba boletše dikanegelo tša dipoelo tša go dula ka gae go maphelo a batho le dikgwebo tša bona.
tgt: balandzise tindzaba tekuvalelwa lokukhulu kwavelonkhe ngetimphilo tebantfu kanye nemabhi zinisi abo.

src: ba ile metseng, di toropong le ditoropokgolong, ba tšweletša dikanegelo tša batho ba ba tlwaelegilego gomme ba gogela šedi ya setšhaba go mathata ao go itemogetšwego wona maoke long le dikliniking, gomme seo se hlohleleditše magato a mmušo.
tgt: bebaphumile basemimangweni, emado lobheni nakumadolobhakati, bagcogca baletsa tindzaba tebantfu labetayelekile baphindze futsi benta kutsi livelonkhe linake tinkinga tibhedlela nemitfolamphilo lehlangabetana nato, letenta kutsi hulumende atsatse tinyatselo.

src: bobegaditaba bja rena bo utollotše dilo tšeo ka tlwaelo di bego di ka se utollwe.
tgt: betindzaba betfu baphi ndze futsi basikhanyisela basikhombisa tintfo lebeku ngenteka ngalokwetayele kile kutsi besingeke sitibone.

src: ba phethagaditše mošomo wa bona wa bohlokomedi ka go tšweletša nyanyeng mediro ya bomenetša le taolompe, e lego seo se bakilego ngangišano ye kgolo ya setšhaba gomme se sa dira gore go be le dinyakišišo tša maemo a godimo tše mmalwa.
tgt: bafezekise umsebenti wabo wekuba ngulabagadzile ngekutsi bavumbulule tento tenkhohlakalo nekusetje ntiswa kabi kwemali yahu lumende, lokuvutsele inkhu lumomphikiswano lenkhulu yavelonkhe lokubese kuhole la kuluphenyo loluphakeme kakhulu.

src: ka di pego tše ba dirile gore batho ba be le kholofelo go bona.
tgt: ngako lokubika batfole kwetsenjwa bantfu.

src: bobegaditaba bjo bo lokologilego ga se mafelelo ka bobjona.
tgt: tetindzaba letikhululekile atigcini ngato kuphela.

src: ke mokgwa woo temokrasi e bolokwago le go thekgwa ka ona.
tgt: yindlela yekutfola nekugci na intsandvo yelinyenti.

src: nakong ya leuba le, bobegaditaba bja rena ga se bja kgatha fela tema ya bohlokomedi, eupša bo phethagaditše mošomo wa bjona wa segae wa go thekga maitapišo a setšhaba go laola coronavirus .
tgt: ngesikhatsi salolubhubhane, betindzaba betfu abakadlalinje kuphela indzima yabo leyetayelekile yekucaphe la, kepha bente umsebenti wabo wekwesekela umtamo wavelonkhe kute kutsi kulawulwe leligciwane lecorona .

src: go lebeletšwe bohlokwa bja bobegaditaba temokrasing ya rena, ke matshwenyego a magolo gore go swana le makala a mangwe a ekonomi, mathata a coronavirus a amile kudu makala a bobegaditaba bja rena.
tgt: uma kubukwa kubaluleka kwebetindzaba kutemphilo yentsandvo yetfu yelinye nti, kuyintfo lekhatsatana kakhulu kutsi yonkhe lemi nye imikhakha yetemnotfo, lenhlekelele yeligciwane lecorona lihlasele kamatima tindlu tikhungo tetfu tebeti ndzaba.

src: diphatlalatšo tše dingwe di lahlegetšwe ke 60% ya letseno la tšona ka matšatši a mathomo a go dula ka gae.
tgt: letinye tishicilelwa tilahlekelwe ngemaphe senti lange60 emali yato lengenako emalangeni eku cala ekuvalwa lokukhulu kwavelonkhe.
