src: go ya ka mokgatlo wa kankere wa afrika borwa (cansa), magareng ga bana ba 800 go fihla go ba 1 000 ba ka afrika borwa ba phekolwa gore ba na le kankere ngwaga o mongwe le o mongwe.
tgt: ngekuya kwenhlangano yaseningizimu afrika yetamdlavuta (icansa), njalo ngemnyaka bantfwana baseningizimu afrika labatfolakala banamdla vuta basemkhatsini walabange800 kuya kulaba 1 000. nanoma kunjalo, lenhlangano ilinganisela ekutsini ihhafu yalaba ntfwana eningizimu afrika abatfolwa.

src: le ge go le bjale, mokgatlo wo o akanya gore seripa gare sa bana bao ba nago le kankere ka afrika borwa ga ba ke ba phekolwa gore ba na le yona.
tgt: kwenta siciniseko sekutsi mdlavuta ubonwa masinyane, ichoc yenta tinhlelo tekucaphelisa emimangweni, itjela batali nebantfwana ngetimphawu letisheshe tibekhona teku caphelisa labafanele kutsi baticaphele.

src: go thuša go netefatša gore kankere e utollwa ka pela ka fao go kgonagalago, choc e sepetša mananeo a temošo ditšhabeng, e botša batswa di le bana ka ga maswao a ka pela a temošo ya kanke re ao ba swanetšego go a hlokomela.
tgt: lenhlangano yesekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labanamdlavuta noma tifo tengati letisongela imphilo kanye nemindeni yabo.

src: setheo se se thekga bana le bafsa ba mahlalagading ba ba nago le kankere goba malwetši a go ba kotsi a madi gammogo le ba malapa a bona.
tgt: "sihlose kusheshe sisi bone lesifo bese siselapha ngemphumelelo.

src: ka nako efe goba efe, choc e ka kgona go hlokomela bana le bafsa ba mahlalagading ba go feta ba 1 500, mola ka go le lengwe e fana ka thekgo ya tša leago go malapa a go feta a 1 500," gwa bolela seegers.
tgt: nanoma ngunini, ichoc ingana kekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labangetulu kwalaba1 500, ibe futsi yesekela ngekwetengcondvo nangekwetenhlalo imindeni lengetulu kwale1 500," kusho seegers.

src: mo ngwageng wa ditšhelete wo o fetilego, seegers o bolela gore choc e kgonne go direla bana ba 1 724, bafsa ba mahlalaga ding ba 553 le batho ba bagolo ba 2 232 ka go diriša mananeo a yona a motheo.
tgt: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, seegers utsi ichoc yakhona kutfula tinsita kubantfwana laba1 724, bantfu labasha laba553 kanye nebantfu labadzala laba2 232 ngetinhlelo tayo letingumgogodla.

src: "ditirelo tša rena di akaretša thekgo ya maikutlo ge ba le gare ba phela le kankere, khomotšo, tlho komelo ya bao ba bakwago le badimo le thekgo ka tša poloko go bao ba hlokofaletšwego," gwa bolela seegers.
tgt: "tinsita tetfu tifaka ekhatsi kwesekelwa ngekwemiva ngesikhatsi basesebukene namdlavuta, kudvudvutwa, kunakekelwa kwaseku pheleni kwemphilo kanye nekwesekelwa uma sewu shonelwe," kusho seegers.

src: maswao a kanke re ya bana ao a reetšwego ka st siluan s – nyaka thušo ya tša kalafo e sa le ka pela mabapi le maswao ao a sa iphodišego.
tgt: timphawu tast siluan tamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni s – funa lusito lwetekwe lashwa kusenesikhatsi lwetinkhomba letichube kako.

src: i – dipatso tše tšhweu ka leihlong, go thoma go leana mahlo, go foufala mo go hlagelelago go na mo goba thaka ya leihlo ye e rurugago.
tgt: i – licashata lelimhlo phe esweni, kufica liso lokusha, kungaboni emehlweni lokuvelenje kwenteke ngekushesha noma kukhukhumuka kwendvumbu yeliso.

src: mpshafatšo ya n3 e matlafatša maafrika borwa owen mngadi mduduzi jijana ke mong wa disability empowerment movement yeo e lego ye nngwe ya dikhamphani tšeo di holegago gabjale go tšwa mpshafatšong ya tsela ya lephefo ya n3 yeo e jelego dibilione tše 26 tša diranta gareng ga pietermaritzburg le durban ka kwazulunatal.
tgt: kutfutfukiswa kwen3 kutfutfukisa bantfu baseningizimu afrika owen mngadi mduduzi jijana longumnikati wenhlangano letfutfukisa labaphila nekukhubateka, lekungulenye yetinkapani letizuzako nyalo kula mabhiliyoni lar26 ekutfutfukisa umgwaco lomkhulu in3 emkhatsini kwemgungundlovu nasethekwini kwazulunatali.

src: projeke ye, yeo e etilwego pele ke ba south african national road agency soc limited (sanral), e netefatša gore baipereki ba bjalo ka jijana ga ba holege feela empa ba hlolela le batho ba bangwe mešomo.
tgt: lomklamo, loholwa yisouth afri can national road agency soc limited (isanral), icinisekisa kutsi bosomabhizinisi labafana najijana abagcini kuphela ngekuzuza kodvwa baphindze bavulele labanye ematfuba emsebenti.

src: jijana, yoo a phelago ka bogolofadi, o re khamphani ya gagwe e tsenya maswao a tsela gareng ga hilton le pietermaritzburg.
tgt: jijana, lophila nekukhubateka, utsi inkapani yakhe isebenta kufaka timphawu temgwaco emkhatsini kwasehilton nasemgungundlovu.

src: yena o thwetše batho ba 13 gomme o re projeke ye e fetotše maphelo a bona.
tgt: ucashe bantfu laba13 futsi utsi lomklamo sewutiguculile timpilo tabo.

src: "bjalo ka batho bao ba phelago ka bogolofadi, re bontšhitše gore re a kgona.

src: molaodi wa mananeo ka sanral n3, tsepo matekane, o re khamphani ya gabo e netefaditše gore dipersente tše 30 tša mošomo di fiwa dikhamphani tša kgauswi tšeo di nago le bokgoni bja go aba ditirelo tša go fapafapana.
tgt: umphatsi waloluhlelo lwesanral n3 tshepo matekane utsi inkapani yakhe icinisekisile kutsi umse benti lo30% waniketwa tinkapani tendzawo letinelikhono lekwenta imisebenti letitsite.

src: se se hlotše menyetla go dikha mphani tše nnyane tšeo beng ba tšona e lego baswa, batho bao ba bego ba gateletšwe peleng mmogo le basadi.
tgt: loku kwavula ematfuba lamanengi kumabhizinisi lamancane laphetfwe lusha, bantfu lebebacindzetelekile kanye nabomake.

src: "go na le dikhamphani tše nnyane, tša magareng le tše nnyanennyane tše 108 tšeo gabjale di šomago ka dipro jekeng tša go fapafapana," a realo.
tgt: "kunemabhizinisi la108 lamancane, lasemkhatsini nalasafufusa kungunyalo lasebenta kumiklamo lehlukahlukene," usho njalo.

src: nokuthula zondi wa ingqalabutho yamalinda multipurpose trading yena o filwe konteraka ya go aba mabu le go tsenya diphaephe tša go gamola meetse.
tgt: nokuthula zondi weingqalabutho yamalinda multipurpose trading waniketwa inkontileka yekuphakela umhlaba nekufaka emaphayiphi ekuhambisa emanti.

src: yena o re khamphani ya gagwe e thwetše batho ba seswai bao ba nago le mabo kgoni, go balwa le baotledi.
tgt: utsi inkapani yakhe icashe bantfu laba8 labanemakhono, labafaka ekhatsi bashayeli.

src: zondi o tlaleletša ka gore basadi ba na le bokgoni bja go swana le bja banna gomme khamphani ya gagwe e na le rekote ya bohlatse bja go laetša bokgoni bja yona bja kabo ya ditirelo.
tgt: zondi ungete watsi bomake nabo banelikhono njengabo babe futsi inkapani yakhe inemlandvo lomuhle wekwenta umsebenti.

src: "re kwešiša bohlokwa bja nako gomme re fihlelela dinepo tša rena go netefatša gore projeke e sepela botse.
tgt: "siyakuvisisa lokubaluleka kwesikhatsi nekugcina sikhatsi lesibekiwe kute sicinisekise kutsi umklamo uhamba kahle ngalokufanelekile.

src: re tloga re leboga monyetla wo gomme re holofela go hwetša e mengwe menyetla gore khamphani ya rena e gole go ya le ka maemo a tša boagi," a tlaleletša ka go realo.
tgt: sibonga kutfola lelitfuba futsi sitsemba kutsi kukhulu lesitakutfola kute sikhulise inkapani yetfu ihambi sane nemazinga etekwakha," wangeta ngekusho njalo lomake.

src: diprojeke tše bohlokwa tša mmušo wa bosetšhaba matekane o bolela gore kaonafatšo ya kgorwana ya tshepetšo ya dithoto le diintaseteri ya durbanfree stategauteng e na le tekanyetšo yeo e ka bago dibi lione tše 26 tša diranta gomme ebile ke ye nngwe ya diprojeke tše bohlokwa tša mmušo wa bosetšhaba tša togamaano e kopantšwego yeo e tsebegago ka la sip2.
tgt: imiklamo lemcoka yahu lumende wavelonkhe matekane utsi lomklamo wekutfutfu kisa lobitwa ngekutsi yidurbanfree state logistics and industrial corridor unesilinganiso sesabelotimali lesitigidzigidzi ler26 futsi ungu lomunye wemiklamo lomcoka wendlelalisu lehlangene yahulu mende wavelonkhe.

src: projeke ye e tla oketša n3 ka bophara bja yona ka go oketša mekgothana go ba e mene goba e mehlano ka mahlakoreng ka moka, gomme le maphamoganomagolo a ditsela a tla be a fetotšwe go kaonafatša kelelo ya sephethephethe.
tgt: lo mklamo utawuvula umgwaco in3 kutsi ube naleminye imizila eluhlangotsini ngalunye.

src: karolo yeo e amegilego ya n3 e be e dutše e itemogela sephethephethe se sentšhi, kudu nakong yeo bontšhi bja difatanaga di tla bego di le tseleng, ka baka la bontšhi bja dilori tša go rwala merwalo go tloga lebopong la durban di šomiša tsela ya lephefo go ya gauteng le diprofenseng tše dingwe tša ka gare ga naga.
tgt: uphindze umbandzakanye kuguculwa kwe kuchumana kwemigwaco lemikhulu kute kutfutfukiswe kuhamba kahle kwetigitjelwa nangekukhululeka.

src: go bile gape le palo e ntšhi ya dikotsi tša tsela tšeo di hlotšwego ke baotledi ba dilori tša go rwala merwalo bao ba sa hlokomelego ge ba feta moo tsela e tepogago ka pejana.
tgt: sigaba lesitsintsekako semgwaco in3 kuleminyaka leyengcile besine kumphintjana kwetigitjelwa, kakhulu ngetikhatsi letiphitsitelako ngoba linyenti letitfutsi temitfwalo lemikhulu letichamuka elugwini lasethekwini tisebentisa lomgwaco kuya egauteng nakuletinye tifundza letisemkhatsini kwalelive.

src: "ntle le go rarolla bothata bja sephethephethe ka go kaonafatša tshepelo ya difatanaga ka go aga mekgothana ya tlaleletšo, mpshafatšo ya n3 e tla oketša gape le polokego.
tgt: futsi bekuba netingoti temgwaco letinengi letibangwa bashayeli betitfutsi temtfwalo ngenca yekunganakekeli uma bahamba lapho kune majika lamakhulu.

src: makopano a ditsela ao a sa bolokegago a tla hlangwa leswa," gwa realo matekane.
tgt: "akusiko kuphela kugcwala kwetitfutsi kwamalanga onkhe lokwenta kutsi tigitjelwa tihambe kahle lokusunjululiwe nga lokwakha imizila lengetiwe, kutfutfukiswa kwen3 kutawenta kutsi kwenyuke tekuphepha.

src: sanral e fane ka dikonteraka tše tharo ka kotareng ya mafelelo ya 2021, gomme mošomo wa go aga tsela o thomile gareng ga pherekgo ng le moranang.
tgt: isanral inikete tinkhontileka letintsatfu kulekota leyengcile yemnyaka we2021 umsebenti wacala kwentiwa emkhatsini kwabhimbi dvwane namabasa.

src: dikarolo tšeo di mpshafatšwago gabjale ke ya dikilomitara tše 19 go tloga cato ridge go ya dardanelles yeo e tsebegago ka la umlaas road; ya dikilomitara tše 26.6 go tloga phamoganong ya ditsela ya dardanelles go ya lynnfield park; le ya dikilomitara tše 30 go tloga lynnfield park go ya phamoganong ya ditsela ya ashburton.
tgt: tincenye letitfutfukiswako nyalo sigaba semgwaco lomakhi lomitha (km) la19 losuka ecato ridge ufike edarda nelles, lowatiwa ngekutsi ngumgwaco iumlaas; sigaba semgwaco lesi20.6 km losuka edardanelles inter change kuya elynnfield park; kanye nesigaba semgwaco lesi30km losuka elynnfield park uye eashburton inter change.

src: matekane o hlalosa gore sip2 e tla matlafatša kgorwana ya tshepetšo ya dithoto le dinamelwa gareng ga mafelomagolo a diintaseteri ka afrika borwa, ya kaonafatša phihlelelo e kaone ya mafelo a tša thomelontle le thomelokanageng ka durban gomme ya ba ya dira gore mošomo o sepele botse kgorwaneng yeo.
tgt: matekane utsi isip2 itawukhulisa lomgwaco weti gitjelwa newetekutfutswa kwemphahla losemkhatsini kwemahabhu etimboni la mcoka aseningizimu afrika, itawutfutfukisa kufinyelela kutinsita tekuhanjiswa nekunge niswa kwemphahla letisethekwini futsi itawu khuphula lizinga lekusebenta ngendlela lekahle kule phaseji.

src: o tlaleletša ka gore projeke ye ke karolo ya leano la tlhabollo la bosetšhaba la 2030 mmogo le leanolegolo la dinamelwa la bosetšhaba la 2050 gomme e thekga leano la kagoleswa le tsošološo ya ikonomi la mmušo.
tgt: ungete ngekutsi lomklamo uyincenye yeluhlelo lwavelonkhe lwentfu tfuko lwemnyaka we2030 neluhlelo lolukhulu letekutfutsa lwemnyaka we2050 futsi usekela luhlelo lwahulumende lwekwakha kabusha nele kuvuselela umnotfo.

src: ka go realo, mmušo o ikemišeditše go tla ka lenaneo la dinamelwa leo le sepelelanago le dihlokwa tša batho bao ba phelago ka afrika borwa gomme ebile le kgontšhago batho gore ba se šomiše tšhelete e ntšhi ge ba tšea maeto.
tgt: kute kube ngunyalo, hulumende uhlose kutfu tfukisa luhlelo lwetekutfutsa lolutawuhambisana neti dzinga tangemphela tebantfu labahlala eni ngizimu afrika futsi lutawu bonelela bantfu labanemali lencane lebayisebentisela kukhokhela tindleko teku hamba.

src: bjala bo ka ba kotsi bophelong bja ngwana yoo o mo imilego vukuzenzele unnamed basadi ba baimana ba na le maikarabelo a gore ba se nwe ka baka la gore bjala bo ka hlola bolwetši bjoo bo amago tlhabologo ya ngwana.
tgt: tjwala bungalimata imphilo yemntfwana wakho asengakatalwa vukuzenzele unnamed bomake labakhulelwe banemsebenti weku tivikela banganatsi tjwala ngoba bungabanga sifo lesitsikameta kukhula kwemntfwana.

src: se ke go ya ka motlatšatona wa tlhabollo ya leago, hendrietta bogopanezulu yoo a tsebagaditšego lenaneo la tshebotšo la 999 foetal alcohol spectrum disorder (fasd).
tgt: loku kushiwo lisekela lendvuna yetekufutfukisa tenhlalo, hendrietta bogo panezulu, losandza kucala luhlelo lwekulwa nesifo i999 foetal alcohol spectrum disorder (ifasd).

src: maikemišetšo a lesolo le ke go hlohleletša ditšhaba go thuša go šireletša masea ao a sešogo a belegwa ka go ruta batho, kudu basadi bao ba lego mengwageng ya go dira bana, ka ga dikotsi tša go nwa mola ba imile goba ba nyantšha.
tgt: inhloso yalomkhankhaso kugcugcutela imimango kutsi isite kuvikela bantfwana lebasengakabelekwa ngekufundzisa bantfu, kakhulu bomake labasakhona kubeleka, mayelana nebu ngoti bekunatsa tjwala ube ukhulelwe noma usamu nyisa.

src: "go bohlokwa gore basadi ka moka bao ba imilego mmogo le bao ba nyakago go bona ba belega bana bao ba phetšego botse ba efoge go nwa bjala.
tgt: "kumcoka kutsi bonkhe bomake labakhulelwe nalabo labanesifiso sekutala bantfwana labaphile kahle bayekele kunatsa tjwala.

src: kotsi yeo e hlolwago ke fasd ke ya go ya go ile ebile ga e dirolloge, gomme bana bao ba belegwa go ba na le bolwetši bjo ba ba le mathata ao a amago mmele le monagano," gwa realo motlatšatona bogopanezulu nakong ya tsebagatšo.
tgt: umonakalo lobangwa yifasd uba wemphilo yonkhe futsi awubuyiseleki emuva, futsi bantfwana labatalwa nalokugula baba netinkinga tasemtimbeni netasengco ndvweni," kwasho lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu emcimbini wekwetfulwa kwaloluhlelo.

src: yena o tlaleleditše ka gore afrika borwa e tsebega ka go ba le bothata bja go nwa bjala kudu, gomme naga ye e gareng ga dinaga tšeo di nwago bjala gampe lefaseng.
tgt: wangeta ngekutsi iningi zimu afrika yatiwa ngekuba nenkinga yekunatsa tjwala, lelive libalwa njengalamanye lamabi lahamba embili emhlabeni ngenca yemazinga alo ekunatsa tjwala.

src: motlatšatona bogopanezulu o sa tšwa go etela dikarolo tšeo di fapafapanego tša naga a ruta basadi ka ga dikotsi tša go nwa ba imile, e le karolo ya lesolo la 999 fasd.
tgt: lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu usandza kuhambela tincenye letehlukahlukene talelive letfu, afundzisa bomake mayelana nebungoti bekunatsa tjwala bakhulelwe njengencenye yemkhankaso we999 fasd.

src: ge a be a le boitekong ka rustenburg ka profenseng ya leboabodikela, o boditše badudi ba fao gore maemo a tšhomišompe ya bjala ka lekeišeneng leo a a tšhoša.
tgt: lesikhatsi aseboitekong erustenburg enyakatfo nshonalanga, watjela takhamuti kutsi lizinga leku setjentiswa kabi kwetjwala emalokishini liyesabeka.

src: moimana wa kgwedi tše nne yoo gape e lego modudi wa boiketlong, basetsana tlalang (28), yoo a tsenetšego le lengwe la masolo, o rile o lesitše go nwa ka botlalo ge a se no lemoga gore o imile, gomme a be a re o tsenela disešene tša tshedimošo ya pele ga pelego kliniking.
tgt: make lonetinyanga letine akhulelwe lohlala eboite kong, basetsane tlalang (28), lobekahambele lomunye walemikhankaso, utse wayekela futsi wagcina ngci kunatsa emva kwekutfola kutsi ukhulelwe futsi watsi sewuhambela emaseshini asemtfolamphilo elwatiso newesikhatsi lesandvulela kubeleka.

src: yena o hlohleleditše baimana ba bangwe go lesa gonabjale go nwa bjala le go lesa go šomiša diokobatši.
tgt: uncusa labanye bomake labakhulelwe kutsi bayekele leso sikhatsi kunatsa tjwala nekusebentisa tidzakwamiva.

src: go lwela go aga afrika borwa ye e laetšago tlhompho go ditokelo tša botho vukuzenzele unnamed ka la 12 lewedi 1977, stephen bantu biko o ile a hlokofala a le kgolegong ya pretoria central.
tgt: umshikashika wekubuyisa ubuntfu eningizimu afrika vukuzenzele unnamed mhla ti12 inyoni 1977, ste phen bantfu biko washona agcinwe maphoyisa ejele lelatiwa ngepretoria central prison.

src: seriti sa motho, e lego kokwane yeo e bego e le pelong ya bolwelatokologo bja gagwe bja phahlogo ya bathobaso, o ile a se tingwa.
tgt: sitfunti sebuntfu, leku simiso lesihamba embili kulobushoshovu bakhe bekubuyisa sitfunti semuntfu lomnyama, sacekelwa phasi.

src: ka mantšu a ramolao wa lapa, sir sydney kentridge, lehu la gagwe e bile "le sehlogo la bodutu godimo ga mmetse lebatong la leswika ka seleng ya kgolego".
tgt: ngekwemagama emmeli wemndeni wakhe sir sydney kentridge, "kushona kwakhe bekubuhlungu kakhulu futsi bekayedvwa ashonela emethini lephasi esemendeni yelijele."

src: e sa dutše e le tiragalo ya masetlapelo le ka morago ga mengwaga ye ka moka ge re gopola gore steve biko o be a na le mengwaga e 30 feela ge a hlokofala.
tgt: kutawuhlala kuyintfo lebanga lusizi lolukhulu emva kwayo yonkhe leminyaka leyengcile, kukhumbula kutsi steve biko bakaneminyaka le30 kuphela uma ashona.

src: bophelo bja gagwe bo ile bja fedišwa ke bao ba bego ba tšhaba maatla le kwalakwatšo ya dikgopolo tša gagwe tša boitokollo mmogo le maitekelo a gagwe a go hlahlelela banna le basadi ba bathobaso ka boikgantšho le seriti.
tgt: wabulawa asengakafiki esicongweni semphilo yakhe ngilabo bebasaba emandla ekubona imibono yakhe lesetulu yekutikhulula kanye nemitamo yekufaka kumuntfu lomnyama kutitsandza nekuba nesitfunti emadvodzeni nakubomake besive lesinsundvu.

src: nakong ya go phela ga gagwe ga sa ka a bona seo a bego a se bitša ‘sefoka sa go phadima’, e lego boitemogelo bja botho bja nnete.
tgt: azange akhone kubona ekuphileni kwakhe loko lokubitwa ngekutsi ‘ngumklomelo lokhatimu lako", lekukubona buntfu bangemphela.

src: ge a be a ngwala ka kgopolo ye, o ile a bolela mantšu a a go tuma: "ge nako e dumela re tlo ba seemong seo re kgonago go fa afrika borwa mpho e botsebotse ka moo go kgonegago, e lego sefa hlego sa go laetša botho.
tgt: abhala ngalomcondvo, kwadvuma kutsi watsi: "ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi sitawukhona kupha iningizimu afrika sipho lesikhulu kunato tonkhe – kukhulisa sitfunti sebuntfu."

src: "ge re se no thopa tokologo ka 1994, re kwešišitše gore tokelo ya go bouta ke ye nngwe ya dikarolo tša ntwa ya rena ya go lwela seriti sa motho.
tgt: uma sincoba sitfola inkhu luleko yetfu ngemnyaka we1994, besivisisa kutsi lilungelo lekuvota liyincenye leyodvwa yemzabalazo wetfu wekutfola sitfunti sebuntfu.

src: mengwaga e 28 re le ka gare ga demokrasi, re lebagane le ditlhotlo tše ntšhi tše bjalo ka bodiidi, tlhokego ya mešomo le go se lekalekane.
tgt: eminyakeni lemashumi lamabili nesiphohlongo singene kuntsandvoye linyenti, sihlangabetene netinseyeya letinyenti, letifana nebuphuya, kuswelakala kwemisebenti nekungalingani.

src: ka baka la seo, re fela re palelwa ke go bona gore re tšwa kgole bjang ge go etla phethagatšong ya diko kwane tšeo molaotheo wa rena o theilwego go tšona gomme ebile di sepelelanago thwii le dikgopolo le dithuto tša steve biko.
tgt: ngenca yaloko, sivamise kunga boni kutsi sisuka khashane kanganani kute sikhone kufeza timiso letisisekelo semtsetfosisekelo wetfu futsi letichumanisa imicondvo netifundziso tasteve biko.

src: ka 1977 mmušo wa pelo e mpe o bolaile yo mongwe wa batho bao ba bego ba laetša boetapele ka go mo tima dijo, meetse le kalafo yeo a bego a e hloka ka tšhoganetšo ka baka la go bethwa ošoro ke maphodisa a mmušo wa kgethollo.
tgt: ngemnyaka we1997, umbuso lobewungenalu velo wabulala lomunye umholi walelive lakitsi lobekatse mbisa kakhulu ngekumncisha kudla, emanti kanye nekwelashwa lobe kakudzinga kakhulu ngenca yekushaywa kabuhlungu ngemaphoyisa elubandlu lulo.

src: morago ga mengwaga e 20, kahlolong ya 1997, kgoro tsheko ya molaotheo e boletše gore go phethagatša ditokelo tša motheo tša modudi yo mongwe le yo mongwe gape le go lwela go fihlelela ditokelo tša bona tša leago le ikonomi ke kokwanekgolo ya setšhaba sa go phela ka demokrasi seo se nepilego go tsošološa seriti seo se se lobilego.
tgt: emva kweminyaka lemashumi lamabili, sincumo senkantolo semnyaka we1997, inkantolo yemtsetfosisekelo yatsi kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu nekutfola ema lungelo abo etemnotfo kuluphawu lwemmango wentsandvoyelinyenti loluhlose kubuyisela sitfunti lesilahlekile.

src: lehono ka mo afrika borwa re tšwela pele go šoma go phethagatša ditokelo tša motheo tša moafrika borwa yo mongwe le yo mongwe gore a kgone go phela bophelo bja boleng bja go hloka malwetši, tlala le bohloki.
tgt: namuhla eningizimu afrika, siyachubeka kuse bentela kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu waseningizimu afrika kute baphile imphilo lesezingeni lenge nato tifo, indlala nekuswela.

src: mebušo ya go latelana ya demokrasi e phethagaditše melao ya go tsošološa seriti seo se lobilwego sa bontšhi bja badudi ba ka mo nageng ka go aba thuto, tlhokomelo ya maphelo, dintlo le ditirelo tša motheo.
tgt: imibuso yentsandvoye linyenti lelandzelanako isebentise imitsetfomigomo leletsa sitfunti sebantfu balelive lebesilahlekile ngekubanika imfundvo, kunakekelwa kwetemphilo, tindlu kanye netinsita letisi sekelo.

src: lehono ka mo afrika borwa thuto ya go tšea botse ke tokelo ya motheo.
tgt: namuhla eningizimu afrika, kutfola imfundvo lesezingeni kulilungelo lelisisekelo.

src: mmušo o beeletša ka kaonafatšong ya thuto ya digotlane e le ge o thekga dinepo tša go ithuta tša badudi ba ka nageng ba bannyanennyane, gomme ebile o fana ka kimollo ya leago ka mokgwa wa mananeo a phepo dikolong go netefatša gore barutwana ba bannyane ba fihlelela dinepo tše kaonekaone ka moo go kgonegago.
tgt: hulumende utjale timali kumfundvo legcile ekukhuliseni kahle bantfwana, ekusekeleni imiphumela yetifundvo ebantfwaneni balelive lakitsi labasesebancane, futsi kusita ummango ngeluhlelo leku phakela bantfwana kudla etikolweni kucinisekisa kutsi bafundzi labasesebancane batfola imiphumela lesetulu.

src: ka sekhwama sa bosetšhaba sa thušo ya tšhelete go baithuti (nsfas) mmogo le mehuta e mengwe ya dithekgo tša go tšwa go mmušo, diketekete tša baswa ba maafrika borwa go tšwa malapeng a go ihlokela di kgonne go ba dingaka, boramolao, barutiši, borasaense, diathisene le baipereki.
tgt: ngalesikimu savelonkhe selusito lwetimali kuba fundzi nangaletinye tinhlobo telusito lwahulumende, tinkhulungwane tebantfu labasha baseningizimu afrika labavela eminde nini lephuyile bakhonile kuba bodokotela, bammeli, bothishela, bososayensi, emaathizeni nabosomabhi zinisi.

src: mmušo o thekga badudi bao ba ihlokelago ebile ba sa bolokegago ka mananeo a polokego ya leago gomme ebile o fana ka menyetla ya mešomo ka mananeo a setšhaba a thwalo ya batho ba bantšhi.
tgt: hulumende usekela takhamuti letibutsakatsaka ngekusebentisa tinhlelo tekusita emakhaya laphuyile futsi iniketa ematfuba emisebenti ngaletinhlelo tahulumende tekucasha bantfu labanengi.

src: ka afrika borwa ya kgatelelo yeo steve biko a hlokofaletšego ka go yona, tokologo ya polelo e be e ileditšwe gomme bolwelatokologo bja dipolotiki bo be bo dira gore motho a golegwe goba a kwešwe bohloko le go feta fao.
tgt: kuleningizimu afrika lebeyicindzetela leyabulala steve biko, bekute kukhu luma ngekukhululeka kantsi kuba sishoshovi kutepolitiki bekuholela ekutseni uboshwe ngaphandle kwekushushiswa noma ubulawe.

src: lehono ka mo afrika borwa baswa bao ba lego mengwageng yeo steve a bego a le go yona, le ba mengwaga ya ka tlase ga yeo, ba di goga pele tšweletšongpele ya merero yeo e lego kgauswi le pelo tša bona, gomme ba kgona go kopana ntle le go tlaišwa goba go iletšwa.
tgt: namuhla eningizimu afrika, bantfu labasha labaneminyaka lelingana naleyo bekanayo steve biko noma lemincane kunaleyo bahamba embili kutebu shoshovi betintfo leti sedvute nabo, futsi bayakhona kutihlela kahle ngekukhululeka ngaphandle kwekuhlukunyetwa noma kwekudzingiswa.

src: tokologo ya polelo le ya gore motho a be karolo ya seo a se ratago, tokelo ya go gwanta mmogo le tokelo ya tekatekano pele ga molao di ama bohle.
tgt: kukhu luma nekuhlanganyela ngekukhululeka, lilungelo lekubhikisha kanye nelilungelo lekulingana ngembi kwemtsetfo ku yalandzelwa kubo bonkhe bantfu.

src: bjalo ka naga, re tšwa kgole ge go etla phethagatšong ya seriti sa motho, e lego kokwane yeo steve biko a bego a e rata kudu.
tgt: sisive, sihambe libanga lelidze kute siphumelele kutfola sitfunti sebuntfu, lekusimiso besihlonishwa ngusteve biko.

src: le ge go le bjalo, re sa na le leeto le letelele leo re tlo le tšeago.
tgt: kodvwa, sisanendlela lendze leku mele siyihambe.

src: go hloka mošomo, go hloka ntlo, mohlagase, meetse a pompi, go hloka naga, go hloka mabokgoni goba menyetla, go dira gore dimilione tša maafrika borwa di palelwe ke go fihlelela maphelo ao ba a nyakago ebile a ba swanelago.
tgt: kungasebenti, kungabi nendlu, nagezi noma emanti lahambako, kungabi nemhlaba, kungabi nemakhono noma ematfuba, tigidzi tebantfu baseningizimu afrika basengakayitfoli imphilo lebafuna kuyi phila.

src: ke ka fao mmušo o šomago le bašomišanimmogo go tša leago go aga ikonomi yeo e akaretšago, go hlola mešomo, go kgontšha di kgwebo go gola, gape le go lwa le bodiidi le tlala.
tgt: kungako hulu mende asebentisana nebalingani betemnotfo kute kwakhiwe umnotfo lofaka wonkhe umuntfu, kwakhiwe ematfuba emisebenti, kuncedvwe emabhizinisi aphumelele futsi kuliwe nebuphuya nendlala.

src: lenaneo la matlafatšo le buša kholofelo owen mngadi lenaneo la matlafatšo ya batšwasehlabelo la thohoyandou (tvep) le lwela go bušetša kholofelo le boitshepo ka gare ga lenaneo la toka ka mananeo a lona a go tsenelela ao maikemišetšo a ona e lego go thuša baphologi ba dikgaruru tša go thewa godimo ga bong (gbv) le ba go katwa ka go ba fa ditirelo tša monagano le tša leago.
tgt: luhlelo lwekunika bahlukunyetwa emandla lubuyisa litsemba owen mngadi luhlelo lasethohoya ndou lwekunika bahlu kunyetwa emandla (itvep) lufuna kubuyisa litsemba nekutitsemba kuluhlelo lwetebulungiswa ngekusebentisa tinyatselo talo letinemandla letihlose kusita labo labasindzile kuludlame lolumayelana netebulili (igbv) nasekudlwengulweni ngekubanika tinsita tetengco ndvo.

src: tvep e thomile ka limpopo mengwaga ya ka godimo ga ye 20, gomme e šomela ka dipetlele tša donald fraser le tshilidzini ka fase ga mmasepala wa selegae wa thulamela.
tgt: letvep leyacalwa elimpo po eminyakeni lema20 leye ngcile, isebentela etibhedlela itshilidzini nedonald fraser letingaphasi kwamasipala wasekhaya ithulamela.

src: molaodimogolo wa tvep wa motšwaoswere, fhatuwani manthada, o re maikemišetšo a yona ke go hlohleletša maikutlo a go se amogele tlaišo ya thobalano, ya gbv le tlaišo ya bana magareng a badudi ba thohoyandou, ka lebaka la gore ditiragalo tše ke tše ntši kudu ka tikologong ye.
tgt: libamba lemcondzisi waloluhlelo fhatuwani manthada utsi loluhlelo luhlose kufaka indlela yekubuka tintfo lengavumeli nakancane kutsi kube nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwemacansi, ngekwegbv kanye nekwebantfwana kuletakhamuti tasethohoyandou, ngoba kuliciniso lelimsulwa kutsi loluhlobo lwemacala ayenteka kulendzawo.

src: o re mo nakong ye e fetilego, dipalopalo tša bosenyi di be di tle di laetše gore go na le melato ye mentši ya go katwa ka thohoyandou, eupša tvep e tšeere magato a mantši mo go oketšeng temošo le go fa ditirelo tša thobamatswalo ya letšhogo go thibela thogako ye.
tgt: utsi esikhatsini lesengci le, lubalobalo lwemacala beluvamise kukhomba kutsi bewamanengi emacala ekudlwengula ethohoyandou, kodvwa itvep ibe neligalelo lelikhulu ekuletseni lwatiso nekunika bantfu tinsita tekwelulekwa ngekuhlukumeteka kute kuliwe nalomkhuba lomubi.

src: ka ge lefase le tla be le keteka lesolo la ntwa ya matšatši a 16 a tlhokego ya dintwa kgahlanong le basadi le bana go tloga ka 25 dibatsela go fihla go 10 manthole, mathanda o re lenaneo le kgotsofaditše kgatelopele ye e dirilwego ka go hlohleletša badudi go kwešiša ditokelo tša bona le go bega bosenyi.
tgt: njengoba umhlaba wonkhe utawube ubuke lomkhankhaso wetinsuku leti16 tebushoshovi bekucedza ludlame lolubhekiswe kubomake nasebantfwaneni kusuka mhla ti25 lweti kuya kumhla ti10 ingongoni, manthada utsi loluhlelo lunelisekile ngaloku leselikwentile lekukugcugcutela takhamuti kutsi tiwavisise emalungelo ato nekutsi tibike uma kwenteka emacala.

src: "tvep e amogela batšwasehlabelo ba dikgaruru tša ka malapeng ba palo ya gare ga 80 le 100 kgwedi ye nngwe le ye nngwe, mola melato ya go katwa ye 45 go fihla go 50 e begwa kgwedi ye nngwe le ye nngwe," go bolela manthada.
tgt: "letvep itfola bahlukunye twa beludlame lwasekhaya labasemkhatsini kwe80 ne100 njalo ngenyanga, bese kuba macala ekudlwengulwa la45 kuya ku50 labikwa njalo ngenyanga," kusho manthada.

src: disenthara tša ditirelo ka moka tša lenaneo di fa batšwasehlabelo ditirelo tša go fapanafapana, go akaretšwa go fihlelela thušo ya semolao, tšhireletšo ya batšwasehlabelo kgahlanong le batshwenyi, tlhokomelo ya melato ya kgorotsheko, thobamatswalo le matlafatšo ka tlhabollo ya bokgoni, bjalo se se fa batšwasehlabelo sebaka sa go thoma ka boswa.
tgt: sikhungo lesisodvwa lesiphetse konkhe kwalolu lelo siniketa tinsita letehluka hlukene kubahlukunye twa, letifaka ekhatsi lusito lwetemtsetfo, kuvikeleka kwebahlukunyetwa kulabo lababahlukumetako, kula ndzelela emacala lasenkantolo, kwelulekwa nekuniketwa emandla ngekusebentisa luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa emakhono, ngaloko bahlukunyetwa batfola litfuba lekucala kabusha.

src: manthada o bolela gore tvep e šomišana kudu le tirelo ya afrika borwa ya sephodisa, kgoro ya maphelo le kgoro ya tlhabollo ya leago go thibela letšhogo la morago ga tlaišo la batšwasehlabelo ba ba swaraganego le go bula molato.
tgt: manthada utsi letvep isebenta ngekubambisana nebetemisebenti yetemapho yisa aseningizimu afrika, litiko letemphilo kanye nelekutfutfukiswa kwemma ngo kute kuvikelwe kutsi bahlukunyetwa bangaphindzi bahlukumeteke kwesibili ngalesikhatsi bavula emacala.

src: "mo melatong ya go katwa, bašomi ba tlhokomelo ya maphelo le maphodisa ba tla disenthareng tša tvep go thuša batšwasehlabelo gore ba bule melato ya bosenyi kgahlanong le batshwenyi gomme gape, go fa ditirelo tša thobamatswalo," a realo.
tgt: "emacaleni ekudlwengula, basebenti betemphilo nema phoyisa beta etikhungweni tetvep kutosita bahlukunye twa bavule emacala bavulele labo lababahlukumetako futsi, babanika tinsita tekwelulekwa," usho njalo.

src: tvep e amogela batšwasehlabelo ba go fihla go matšatši a 14, efela, peakanyo e ka katološwa mo go melato yeo e akaretšago bana le lapa ka moka.
tgt: itvep ihlalisa labo labahlukumetekile kute kufike etinsukwini leti14, kodvwake, loluhlelo lwekuhlaliswa lungalulwa emacaleni lafaka umndeni wonkhe noma bantfwana.

src: "re na le masolo a go hlahlelela badudi ka tsebo ao ka ona re boledišanago le setšhaba le go ruta batho ka ditokelo tša bona.
tgt: "sineyunithi yekunika emandla lehamba icocisana nebantfu futsi ibafundzise mayelana nemalungelo abo.

src: re thuša badudi ba go feta milione ba thohoyandou le ba metse ye mengwe ya kgauswi.
tgt: sisebentela bantfu labatakha muti tasethohoyandou nemaphetselo labangetulu kwesigidzi.

src: re kgonne go bušetša kholofelo gomme bjale batho ba na le tshepo mo go lenaneo la toka ka lebaka la ka fao re amanago ka gona le maphodisa," a realo.
tgt: itvep futsi ivulele bantfu laba44 ematfuba emsebenti labasebentela ematiko lahlukahlukene lafana nelitiko letetimali, letebasebenti nelekwenta luhlolo.

src: tvep gape e hlotše mešomo ya batho ba 44 setheong sa yona bao ba šomelago dikgo ro tša yona tša go fapana go swana le ya ditšhelete, ya merero ya bašomi le ya tekolo.
tgt: nanoma loluhlelo luhlala lutfola imali ler90 000 ngekota lebuya kulitiko lwetekutfutfukiswa kwe mmango laselimpopo, itvep yatsintseka kabi ngecovid19 ngoba bonkhe labo bebanikela ngetimali bahoca, ngaleyondlela taba nemtselela lomubi tinchubo tekusebenta talenhlangano.

src: ka ntle le go amogela thekgo ya ditšhelete ye e tšwelago pele ya r90 000 ka kotara go tšwa go kgoro ya tlhabollo ya leago ya limpopo, tvep e amilwe ke covid19 ka ge bathekgi ka ditšhelete ba bantši ba ikgogetše morago, bjalo se se amile gampe ditshepedišo tša mošomo tša mokgatlo.
tgt: kodvwa, sikhwama sekuphendvula kuludlame lolubhekiswe kubomake nakulabasikati (igbvf), lesasungulwa ngumengameli cyril ramaphosa ngendlovana kulomnyaka, abambisene nenhlangano yabomake yemhlaba yaseningizimu afrika kanye nebalingani bayo kutenhlalo, balusitile loluhlelo.

src: tvep e magareng a sehlopha sa mathomo sa mekgatlo yeo e lwantšhago gbvf, go amogela thekgo ya ditšhelete.
tgt: itvep bekungulolunye lwetinhlangano lebetilwa negbvf lekucala kutfola kusekelwa ngetimali.

src: ka palomoka ya r128 milione yeo e kgobokeditšwego ka dithušo tša lekala la poraebete, sekhwama sa makala a mantši, sekhwama sa gbvf se tla thuša le go thekga phethagatšo ya leanotiro la bosetšhaba la gbvf.
tgt: kunemali letigidzi letir128 leyacokelelwa ngeminikelo levela kumkhakha lotimele, lephuma esikhwameni semikhakha lehlukahlukene, lesikhwama segbvf sitawusita futsi sitawusekela kusetjentiswa kweluhlelo lwendlelalisu yavelonkhe yegbvf.

src: tvep e abetšwe r250 000 ngwaga wo gomme e tla amogela thekgo ye nngwe ya ditšhelete ya 2023. manthada o re ditšhelete tša thekgo di kgontšhitše tvep go fihlelela batšwasehlabelo ba bantši le go dira gore mo kgatlo o tšwelepele go šoma.
tgt: itvep yaniketwa imali yalomnyaka ler250 000 futsi itawuphindze itfole lenye imali ngemnyaka we2023.

src: murendeni vhengani (26) ke mophologi yoo a phološitšwego ke tvep lesoganeng leo a bego a ratana le lona leo le bego le mo tshwenya.
tgt: manthada utsi timali tente kutsi itvep ikhone kufinye lela kubahlukunyetwa labanengi futsi ibe igcina inhlangano isebenta kahle.

src: yena le ngwana wa gagwe wa mengwaga ye mene ba dutše sebaka sa dikgwedi tše 46 mo senthareng ya tvep .
tgt: wacedza tinyanga leti46 ahlala nendvodzakati yakhe leneminyaka lemine kulesi khungo.

src: senthara ye e mo thušitše go bula melato kgahlanong le lesogana le gape le go le bulela taelo ya tšhireletšo.
tgt: lesikhungo samsita ngekutsi akhone kuvulela lisoka lasahlukene nalo emacala nangekutsi akhone kutfola umyalo wasenkantolo weku tivikela kulelisoka.

src: lesogana le le ka se sebaka le sa seka.
tgt: lelisoka lakhe namanje lisaboshiwe.

src: "ba nkamogetše ka diatla tše borutho ka morago ga mengwaga ye mentši ya go tshwenywa.
tgt: "bangemukela ngetandla letifutfumalako emva kwekutsi ngihlupheke iminyaka leminengi.

src: ke kwele ke bolokegile.
tgt: ngativa ngiphe phile.

src: dikgopelo tša nsfas tša 2023 di buletšwe vukuzenzele unnamed saekele ya dikgopelo ya 2023 ya sekema sa bosetšhaba sa thušo ya ditšhelete (nsfas) e buletšwe.
tgt: kuvuliwe kufakwa kweticelo tensfas kwemnyaka we2023 vukuzenzele unnamed kuvuliwe kufakwa kweticelo kusikimu savelonkhe selusito lwetimali sebafundzi (insfas) semnyaka we2023.

src: tona ya kgoro ya thuto ya godingwana, saense le boithomelo, ngaka blade nzimande, o tsebišitše malobanyana ka nako ya kopano ya bobegaditaba.
tgt: indvuna yetemfundvo lephakeme, tesayensi netekusungula, dkt.

src: tona nzimande o re sekema se tšeere sephetho sa go bulela nako ya dikgopelo ka pela, ge go bapetšwa le ngwagola, go fa bakgopedi ba ka moso nako ye e lekanego ya go romela dikgo pelo tša bona le ditokomane tša thekgo.
tgt: blade nzimande, usandza kwetfula lesimemetelo emhlanganweni webetindzaba.

src: ge a e fa pego ya bjalebjale mabapi le thekgo ya ditšhelete ya ngwaga wa ditšhelete wa 2022 wa nsfas, tona nzimande o re tekanetšo ya r43 milione e abetšwe sekema go lefa ditefišo tša baholegi ba thuto, go akaretšwa dijo le putseletšo ya senamelwa, le dimatheriale tša thuto.
tgt: indvuna nzimande utsi lesikimu sincume kutsi kuvulwe lomjikeleto wekufaka ticelo ngembi kwesikhatsi, kute labo labatawufaka ticelo batfole sikhatsi lesanele sekutfumela ticelo tabo kanye nemadokhumenti lahambisana naleto ticelo.

src: o re dikgopelo tše 985 672 di amogetšwe gomme go tšwa go tšona tše 140 636 ga se tša atlega.
tgt: etfula umbiko lomayelana nekuniketwa kwetimali yensfas yemnyaka wekufundza we2022, indvuna nzimande utsi sabelomali lesitigidzigidzi letir43 sabelwa lesikimu kute sikhokhele tindleko tebafundzi tekufundza, letifaka ekhatsi sibonelelo sekudla nesetigitjelwa, kanye nesetinsita tekufundza.

src: go dikgopelo tše di amogetšwego, tše 739 526 di amogetšwe nakwana go thekga ka ditšhelete boingwadišo bjo bo sa letetšwego gore bo feleletšwe go tšwa diinstitšhušeneng tša go fapana.
tgt: utsi batfola ticelo leti985 672 leti140 636 atange tiphumelele.

src: "bontši bja bakgopedi ba ba sego ba atlega ba šitilwe go fa bohlatse bjo bo lekanego bja thekgo ya ditšhelete; ba bangwe ba feta magomo a maswanedi; ge ba bangwe bona ba šetše ba fihleletše maemo a godimodimo a lengwalo la thuto ao nsfas e a thekgago ka ditšhelete gomme maemo a bona ga a sa ba kgontšha go latela dinyakwa tša go ka tsenela thuto ya lekala la kholetše ya tvet," tona nzimande o a hlalosa.
tgt: kuleticelo lebatitfola, leti739 526 tavunywa kwesikhashana, kutawuya ngekutsi bafundzi babhalisile yini kutikhungo lebatikhetsile letehlukahlukene.

src: go ya ka tshedimošo ye e lego weposaeteng ya nsfas, go tloga ka ngwaga wa thuto wa 2021, nsfas ga e sa thekga dithuto tša thuto ya morago ga tikrii ya mathomo ka ditšhelete.
tgt: "linyenti lebafundzi lebafaka ticelo letingatange tiphumelele bahluleka kuletsa bufakazi lobanele lobusekela ticelo tabo tekutfola lusito; betingetulu kwalomkhawulo lobekiwe wekuvumeleka kutfola lolusito; nyalo labafundzi sevele baphumelele kutfola lizinga lelisetulu leticu letikhokhelwa yinsfas futsi bebangahambisani nalendlela yetifundvo temkhakha wemakolishi etvet," kuchaza indvuna nzimande.

src: se se akaretša ditifikeiti tša thuto ya morago ga tikrii ya mathomo, didiploma tša thuto ya morago ga tikrii ya mathomo, ditikrii tša honase, ditikrii tša mastase le phd.
tgt: ngekuya kwelwatiso lolukuwebhusayithi yensfas, kusuka kumnyaka wekufundza we2021, insfas ayisaniketi lusito lwetimali yetifundvo letentiwa emva kwekutfola ticu takho tekucala.

src: se se ra gore lengwalo la thuto la godimodimo leo sekema se le thekgago ka ditšhelete ke tikrii ya mathomo.
tgt: loku kufaka ekhatsi titifiketi letentiwa emuva kwekutfola ticu tekucala, emadiploma lentiwa emuva kwekutfola ticu tekucala, ticu tehonours, temasters netephd.

src: go kaonafatša mokgwa wa dikgopeloka maiteko a go kaonafatša mokgwa wa yona wa go dira dikgopelo le tshepedišo ya tšona go dira gore e be wo mokaonekaone go šomišwa ke bakgopedi bao ba nyakago go dira dikgopelo, tona nzimande o re ngwaga wo, nsfas e dirile diphetogo tše mmalwa tša go kaonafatša mokgwa wo go kgonthišiša gore badiradikgopelo ba se itemogele mathata.
tgt: loku kuchaza kutsi ticu letisetulu letitfola sibonelelo kulesikimu yibachelor’s degree.

src: o re weposaete ya go dira dikgopelo ka inthanete ya nsfas e bopilwe leswa gore e šomišege botse go feta peleng le go dira gore e nyake go swana le dipolatefomo tše dingwe tšeo bakgopedi bao ba nyakago go dira dikgopelo ba di tlwaetšego go swana le whatsapp, twitter, facebook le instagram.
tgt: kutfutfukisa luhlelo lwekufaka ticelokumitamo yekutfutfukisa loluhlelo lwayo kanye netinchubo tekwenta kube malula kulabo labanesifiso sekufaka ticelo, indvuna nzimande utsi kulomnyaka, insfas isebentise tindlela tekutfutfukisa loluhlelo kute kucinisekiswe kutsi konkhe kuhamba ngendlela lefanele.

src: "tshepedišo ya dikgopelo ka boyona e nolofaditšwe gomme dipotšišo tše di botšišitšwego di bonolonyana gore di kwešišwe ke setšhaba.
tgt: utsi lephothali yeinthanethi yekufaka ticelo idizayinwe kabusha kute ikhone kusebentiseka malula futsi ifinyelele nakuletinye tinkhundla labatitayele labo labafuna kufaka ticelo letifana nabowhatsapp, itwitter, ifacebook neinstagram.

src: go tlaleletša, bakgo pedi ba ka kgaotša tshepedišo ya dikgopelo gomme ba tšwela pele ka morago ga sebaka ka ntle le go thoma ka leswa, selo seo se bego se sa kgonege mo dinakong tša go feta, o realo.
tgt: "loluhlelo lwekufaka ticelo kwalona lwentiwe kutsi lube malula futsi imibuto lebutwako bantfu bayayivisisa.

src: "ka godimo ga dikaonafatšo tše di dirilwego, nsfas e okeditše mekgwa ya theknolotši ya go dira dikgopelo go dira gore badiradikgopelo ka go fapana ga bona ba kgone go dira dikgopelo, gape re be re lebeletše gore bontši bja batho bao ba tlago dira dikgopelo ke baswa bao ba ratago go dira dilo ka theknolotši," tona nzimande a tlaleletša.
tgt: lokunye lokwengetiwe, labafaka ticelo bangalumisa kwesikhashana loluhlelo bese bayachubeka emva kwesikhatsi ngaphandle kwekucala phasi, lekuyintfo beyingenteki kulemijikeleto leyengcile, usho njalo.

src: mešomo le menyetla ya mekgwa ya boiphedi milione, gomme palo ye e sa tšwela pele go gola vukuzenzele unnamed ka fase ga mengwaga ye mebedi ya go feta, re thakgotše lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo ya mopresidente go hlola mešomo le go thekga mekgwa ya boiphedišo bjalo ka karolo ya go thekga tsošološo ya ikonomi go tšwa go leuba la covid19.
tgt: imisebenti netindlela tekutiphilisa letigidzi, futsi sisachubeka vukuzenzele unnamed esikhatsini lesingapha nsi kweminyaka lemibili leyengci le, sasungula sikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti kute sivule ematfuba emsebenti nekusekela tindlela tekuphila njengencenye yekusekela kuvuselelwa kwemnotfo ngemuva kwalesikhatsi salo bhubhane wecovid19.

src: lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo ya mopresidente le sa tšwa go atlega go fihlelela bakgathatema ba milione o tee go tloga mola le hlomilwego.
tgt: lesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti sifinyelele kuncophamlandvo yebantfu labasigidzi lababe yincenye kusukela sasungulwa.

src: phihlelelo ye ke ka lebaka la maiteko a tšhomišano mmušong ka moka le setšhabeng ka bophara, go akaretšwa lekala la poraebete, mekgatlo ye e theilwego gare ga setšhaba le ye mengwe ye mentši.
tgt: lemphumelelo ibangwe mitamo lehlangene yawo wonkhe hulumende newawo wonkhe ummango, lefaka ekhatsi umkhakha lotimele, tinhlangano temmango kanye naletinye tinhlangano.

src: lenaneo le na le seabe mo go tlholo ya mešomo mola ikonomi e tšea nako go kaonafala le go hlola mešomo ka palo ye re e nyakago.
tgt: loluhlelo lugcugcutele kwakhiwa kwematfuba emsebenti ngalesikhatsi umnotfo usatsatsa sikhatsi kuvuseleleka nekwakha ema tfuba emsebenti ngelizinga lesilifunako.

src: ge re šogana le kgolo ya ikonomi go hlola mešomo ya seriti le ya go swarelela nako ye telele ka palo ye kgolwane, re tla tšwela pele go kaonafatša katlego, lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo ya mopresidente le go dira gore e oketšega go feta pele.
tgt: njengoba siphikelela ngekukhulisa umnotfo kute isiletsele imisebenti leletsa si tfunti nalesimeme ngelizinga lelikhulu, sitawuchubeka kwakha kulemphumelelo yalesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti futsi sisisabalalise sifike kuyo yonkhe indzawo.

src: go sa nyakega kudu gore go tlaleletšwe tsošološo ya mmaraka wa mešomo.
tgt: namanje kusadzingeka kakhulu kutsi siphelelise kuvuselela timakethe temisebenti.

src: gape e thekga tsošološo ya ikonomi ka ditsela tše bohlokwa.
tgt: lesikhutsati futsi sisekela kuvuselelwa kwe mnotfo ngetindlela letimcoka.

src: go maemo ao e lego gore tlhokego ya bokgoni ke lepheko le legolo mo go khwetšo ya mošomo, mananeo a a fa maitemogelo a mošomo a boleng bja godimo.
tgt: esimeni lapho khona kungabi nesipiliyoni sekwenta umsebenti kulihibe lelikhulu lelenta ungatfoli umsebenti, letinhlelo leti tiniketa sipiliyoni lesisezingeni lelisetulu.

src: ka gare ga lenaneo le legologolo la go thekgwa ke tlhohleletšo, mohlala, baswa ba go batamela go ba 600 000 ba thwetšwe bjalo ka bathušibadikolo ka dikolong tša ka godimo ga tše 22 000 khutlong ye nngwe le ye nngwe ya naga.
tgt: etinhlelweni letinkhulu kakhulu letisekelwe ngalesikhutsati, sibonelo, bantfu labasha labacishe babe ti 600 000 bafakwa etikolweni baba basiti babothishela etikolweni letingetulu kwaleti22 000 letikuyo yonkhe indzawo yelive lakitsi.

src: bolaodi bja sekolo, barutiši le bakgathatema ba bangwe ka moka ba dumela gore seabe sa bathušibadikolo se kaonafaditše tikologo ya go ithuta ka dikolong.
tgt: baphatsi betikolo, bothishela nalabanye balingani bonkhe bavumelana kutsi leligalelo lalabasiti babothishela lente kutsi sibe ncono simo sekufundza etikolweni.

src: batho ba bantši ba ba itšhomelago ba hweditše mekgwa ya bona ya boiphedišo e tsenwe bogare ke leuba.
tgt: bantfu labanengi labatisebentako baphatamiseka kundlela yabo yekuphila ngenca yalobhubhane.

src: lekala la bokgabo lona le amilwe gampe gagolo.
tgt: umkhakha wetebuciko wona watsintseka kakhulu kunaleminye.

src: ka gare ga lekala le, thekgo e filwe batho gore ba ihlolele mešomo gomme ba hlolele le ba bangwe.
tgt: kulomkhakha, bantfu basekelwa kute bativulele ematfuba emsebenti nekutsi bavulele labanye.

src: difilimi, mmino le dipapadi tše di tšweleditšwego bjale di kgona go dira letseno le lengwe go tšwa go thekišo ya ditokelo, ditekete le diroyalethi.
tgt: temafilimu, temculo kanye netemidlalo yaseshashalatini leyakhicitwa nyalo seyiyakhona kwenta imali ngekutsengisa emathikithi nangetinkhokhelo tekusebentisa imisebenti yabo.

src: tše ka moka di bile le seabe kgolong ya lekala.
tgt: konkhe loku bekufaka ligalelo ekukhuliseni lomkha kha.

src: lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo ya mopresidente gape le thekgile mekgwa ya boiphedišo ya nako ye telele.
tgt: lesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti siphindze sasekela kusimamisa tindlela tekuphila.

src: balemelaboiphedišo ba ka godimo ga 140 000 ba amogetše dibaotšha tša thušo ya tšweletšo go ba thuša go thoma le go oketša tšweletšo ka morago ga go tsenwa bogare ke covid19.
tgt: balimi labasafufusa labangetulu kwe140 000 batfola emavawusha ekubasita kutsi bacale kukhicita nekutsi bakhulise imikhicito yabo emva kwekutsikametwa yicovid19.

src: moholegi wo mongwe wo bjalo ke phindile ngcoya wa mengwaga ye 36 go tšwa richmond go la kwazulunatal.
tgt: lomunye walabo labazuza kuloku nguphindile ngcoya loneminyaka le36 waserichmond kwazulunatali.

src: ke o tee wa maloko a lesome a kgwebo ya temo ya lapa gomme o re baotšha ye a e amogetšego e thušitše kgwebo ye mpsha go tšwelapele le go dira poelo.
tgt: ungulomunye wemalunga enhlangano yemndeni yekulima futsi utsi levawusha layitfolile incedzile kutsi lenhlangano lensha ikhone kusindza ingafi nekutsi ikhone kwenta inzuzo.

src: lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo ya mopresidente gape le thekga dialoga, ka menyetla ya go fiwa baoki, dialoga tša saense, batsebi ba mešomo ya diatla le ba bangwe.
tgt: lesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti siphindze futsi sisekele labo labaneticu, lapho khona ematfuba avulekela bonesi, labaneticu tesayensi, bongoti bemakhono kanye nalabanye.

src: diyunibesithi tše masomepeditshela di thuša go thwala dialoga tše di se nago mešomo mo mešomong ye e sepelelanago le mangwalo a bona a thuto.
tgt: emayunivesithi lamashumi lamabili nesitfupha ayasita ngekufaka bantfu labaneticu labangakacashwa emisebe ntini lehambisana neticu tabo.

src: kgoro ya saense le boithomelo e tsebišitše mananeo a saense a badudi a boithomelo a go fapana, go swana le duzi umngeni conservation trust, ye e thwalago baswa ba tikologo bjalo ka dithwadi tša tikologo (envirochamps) go matlafatša ditšhaba gore di tsošološe methopo ya tikologo ya meetse.
tgt: litiko letesayensi neletemisebenti yekuticambela letfule tinhlelo tesayensi letinengi kutakhamuti temisebenti yekuticambela, letifana neduzi umngeni conservation trust, lecasha lusha lwendza wo lube tingcwetfu tekonga simondzawo emaenvirochamps kute lucwashise imimango kutsi ivuselele imitfombo yemanti yendzawo yangakubo.

src: lenaneo le lengwe ka kgoro le thuša borakgwebo go hlabolla ditšhišinyo tša kgwebo ka go ikonomi ya pabalelatikologo.
tgt: lolunye luhlelo lwalelitiko lusita bosomabhizinisi kutsi bente tiphakamiso temabhazinisi letimayelana nemnotfo lovikela simondza wo.

src: mananeo a mešomo ya setšhaba gape a na le khuetšo ye botse ye e lebanego mo go ditšhaba gobane a hlola mošomo go dira setho.
tgt: tinhlelo temmango tekucasha nato tibe nemtselela ngco emimangweni ngoba takha ematfuba emsebenti lazuzisa wonkhe umuntfu.

src: ge go bolelwa ka lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo la mopresidente, se se akaretša go kaonafatša go ithuta ka dikolong, go kaonafatša metsemekutwana, go thekga baphologi ba dikgaruru tša go thewa godimo ga bong, pabalelo ya tikologo le go tšweletša mekgwa ye meswa ya go resaekela matlakala.
tgt: kulesikhu tsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti, loku kufaka kutfutfukisa kufundza etikolweni, kutfutfukisa ti ndzawo tekuhlala letimikhu khu, kusekela labo labasindze kuludlame lolumayelana netebulili, labo labavikela indalo nalabo labeta netindle la letisha tekuvuselela kabu sha imfucuta.

src: lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo la mopresidente le thakgotšwe go rarolla bothata bja tlhokego ya mešomo bjo bo gakaditšwego ke leuba la covid19.
tgt: lesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti satfulwa ngoba kufuneka siphendvule kulenhlekelele yekuswelakala kwemisebenti leyabhebhe tseliswa ngulobhubhane wecovid19.

src: le ge e le gore leuba le ka ba le fedile, tlhoke go ya mešomo ga se e fele.
tgt: nanoma lobhubhane angahle abe ancishisiwe, kuswelakala kwematfuba emsebenti kona akukanciphi.

src: letseno le le amogetšwego mananeong a lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo la mopresidente le bile matlafatšo ya ikonomi go di kgwebo tše nnyane le dikgwe bo tše e sego tša semmušo ka diikonoming tša tikologo go kgabaganya naga.
tgt: imiholo leholwe kuletinhlelo tesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti itfutfukise umnotfo kubosomabhizinisi labancane nakuminotfo yendzawo kulo lonkhe live lakitsi.

src: bathušibadikolo ba ba thwetšwego ka umgungundlovu ba šomiša meputso ya bona ka umgu ngundlovu.
tgt: balekeleli babothishela labacashwe emgungundlovu basebentisa imali yabo emgungundlovu.

src: go bjalo le ka putsonderwater.
tgt: kwenteka kanjalo naseputso nderwater.

src: sebakeng sa go ba le lenaneo la gore ‘batho bao ba hlokago ba tla holega ge bao ba humilego ba huma le go feta’, tšhelete e tsenywa thwii ka gare ga diatla tša ditšhaba tšeo di e hlokago kudu.
tgt: kunekutsi kube nemtselela "wekucala etulu wehlele phasi", imali ifakwe ngco etandleni temimango lapho idzingeka khona kakhulu.

src: tšhelete yeo morago e dikologa mo tulong ya bona gomme morago e ‘boele e tsene go ikonomi ka bophara’.
tgt: leyo mali ibese iyatungeleta kuleyo ndzawo yabese "ikhuphukela enhla" iya kumnotfo lobanti.

src: ke ka lebaka leo re bitšago lenaneo le gore ke la tlhohleletšo, gobane ikonomi ka moka e a holega gotee le setšhaba.
tgt: kungako loku sikubita ngekutsi sikhutsati, ngoba tonkhe tinhlaka temnotfo tiyazuza kanye nemmango.

src: ka lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo la mopresidente, re buletše enetši, boikgafo, bohlami, boithomelo le menyetla.
tgt: ngalesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti, sikhonile kuvula ematfuba etemandla, ekutibophelela, ebuciko, ekuticambela nalamanye ematfuba.

src: mo tshepedišong, re aga setšhaba seo se šomago.
tgt: ngaleyonchubo, sakha ummango losebentako.

src: batho ba go feta milione o tee ba holegile thwii.
tgt: bantfu labangetulu kwesigidzi bazuze ngco.

src: batho ba bangwe ba bantši, ka malapeng le ka ditšhabeng tša bakgathatema, ba kwele khuetšo ya tlhohleletšo.
tgt: labanye labanengi, emindenini nasemimangweni yalabo labayincenye yaloku, bayivile imitselela yalesikhutsati.

src: mošomo wa rena bjale ke go oketša le go tseneletša khuetšo ya mošomo wo.
tgt: umsebenti wetfu nyalo ku khulisa nekujulisa umtselela walomsebenti.

src: ke lebaka la lenaneo la tlhohleletšo ya mešomo la mopresidente, bjale re na le makgolokgolo a diketekete tša batho ba go ba le boitemogelo bja mošomo bja mohola.
tgt: ngenca yalesikhutsati samengameli sekwakha ematfuba emsebenti, nyalo sesinebantfu labamakhulu etinkhulungwane labanesipiliyoni lesimcoka sekwenta umsebenti.

src: bontši bja batho ba go bonolo go ba hwetša ka sayouth.
tgt: linyenti lalabantfu laba litfolakala kalula ngekusebentisa inkhundla isayouth.

src: bokamoso bja rena bo laolwa ke go hlalefišwa ga bopapimpana vukuzenzele unnamed go nale ditiragalo tše mmalwa tša kantoro ya mopresidente tša go uša pelo go feta go iketla le bana mesong.
tgt: kutfutfukiswa kwebantfwana kusikhiya lesivula likusasa letfu vukuzenzele unnamed imbalwa kakhulu imisebenti yelihhovi si lamengameli le yenelisanako kwendlula kucitsa sikhatsi saseku seni usemkhatsini kwe bantfwana labancane.

src: malobanyana mo ke tšwa pulong ya senthara ya tlhalefišo ya bomapimpana ya little flower (ecd) gola bizana kua kapa bohlabela fao ke ilego ka iketla le ba bangwe ba baetapele ba kamoso ba naga ya gaborena, ke ba balela le go ba theeletša.
tgt: madvute nje bengiha mbele umcimbi wekuvu lwa kwesikhungo seku tfutfukiswa kwebantfwa na (iecd) ilittle flower ebizana empumalanga kapa, lapho ngicitse khona sikhatsi nalabanye baholi besikhatsi lesitako belive lakitsi, ngibafundzela futsi ngibalalela.

src: senthara ye e satšo agwa ke mokgatlo wa tlhabollo wa impande wa ka mo afrika borwa ka thekgo ya setheo sa nelson mandela.
tgt: lesikhungo sisandza kwa khiwa yinhlangano yekutfu tfukisa iimpande south africa ngekwesekelwa yinelson mandela foundation.

src: ke kgwathile maikutlo ke boikgafo bja bašomedi ba senthara ye ge ba thekga setšhaba le bana ba go tsena go yona.
tgt: ngatsintseka kakhulu nge kutibophelela kwebasebenti balesikhungo ngekutsi base kele ummango nebantfwana bawo.

src: ba mpoditše tša mehleng ya ge senthara ye e thomišwa, ka fao bašomedi ba bego ba sokolela go hwetša meputso ya bona eupša ba tšwelapele go tla mošomong.
tgt: bangitjele ngebu matima labahlangabetana nabo uma sisacalwa lesi khungo, bebanebumatima bekukhokhela basebenti kodvwa bebachubeka beta emsebentini.

src: ba mpoditše gape le gore le ge e le gore batswadi ba be ba sa kgone go lefela bana ba bona tefo ya r20, bana ba be ba sa gomišetšwe morago.
tgt: bangitjele futsi kutsi nanoma imindeni beyihluleka kukhokha ti ndleko temntfwana letir20 umntfwana ngamunye, labo bantfwana bebangajikiswa babuyiselwe emuva ekhaya.

src: boikgafo bja bašomedi ba senthara ye ya ecd bo bohlokwa kudu ka gobane disenthara tša tlhalefišo ya bomapimpana di kgatha tema ye bohlokwa kudu tlhabollong ya setšhaba sa gaborena.
tgt: kutibophelela kwebase benti balesikhungo seecd kumcoka ngoba tikhungo tekutfutfukiswa kweba ntfwana tidlala inzima le nkhulu ekutfutfukiseni sive sakitsi.

src: tšona disenthara tše di hwetšagala motsaneng wo mongwe le wo mongwe, toropong efe goba efe le ditoropong ka moka tše kgolo ka mo nageng.
tgt: letikhungo tinga tfolakala kunoma ngisiphi sigodzi, lidolobha nelidolo bhakati lelikulelive.

src: bontši bja tšona di thomilwe ke basadi mo setšhabeng bao ba bego ba sala ba hlokomela bana ge batswadi ba bona ba ile mešomong.
tgt: tikhungo letinengi tacalwa bomake bemmango kute basite batali lebadzinga kutsi bantfwana babo banakekelwe nga lesikhatsi basesemsebentini.

src: bontši bja tšona disenthara tše di thomile e le dikretšhe goba dise nthara tša go hlokomela bana mosegare.
tgt: linengi laletikhungo tacalwa tisebenta njengetinkhulisa nanjengetikhungo tekushiya bantfwana.

src: tše ntši tša tšona di godile mme gabjale di akaretša lenaneothuto la motheo la dithuto tša mehleng ka gare ga ditirelo tša tšona.
tgt: letinengi setikhulile tatfutfuka kute tikhone kufaka ikharikhulamu yemfundzo lesisekelo kumisebenti yato.

src: bjalo ka mmušo, re tšeere mošomo wa go kaonafatša maemo a tlhokomelo le go dira gore didirišwa di be gona gore disenthara tša ecd di kgone go sepediša ditiragalo tše maleba tša bana go ba lokišetša dithuto tše dumeletšwego ke mmušo.
tgt: njengahulumende, sitse tse sinyatselo sekutfutfu kisa emazinga ekunakekela nekwenta kutsi tinsita titfo lakale kutikhungo teecd kute titakhona kwenta imi sebenti lefanele kubantfwana labancane kute balungele kufundza lokuhlelekile.

src: ka moranang 2022, re kgonne go šutiša ka botlalo tirelo ya ecd go tšwa go kgoro ya tlhabollo ya leago go ya go kgoro ya thuto ya motheo.
tgt: ngamabasa 2022, siwupho tfulile umsebenti weku susa umsebenti weecd kulitiko letekutfutfukiswa kwemmango uye kulitiko lemfundvo lesisekelo.

src: tšhutišo ye e diretšwe go amanya tlhalefišo ya bomapimpana le lenaneothuto la dithuto tše dumeletšwego dikolong kamoka le go aba tlhahlo, thuto le tlhabollo go bašomedi disenthareng tša ecd go potologa naga.
tgt: loku kwentelwa kutsi kuchunya niswe kutfutfukiswa kwe mntfwana kute kube yince nye yekharikhulamu yemfu ndvo lehlelekile neku nika kucecesha, imfundvo nekutfutfukisa basebenti labasetikhungwini teecd letiseveni lonkhe.

src: ka baka la gore dithuto tše tša motheo tša bomapimpana di le bohlokwa katlegong ya ngwana morago ga mengwaga ngwaga, molaophetošwa wa melao ya thuto ya motheo wo gabjale o lego pele ga palamente o šišinya gore e be kgapeletšo go bana ka moka gore ba tsene disenthareng tša ecd tekano ya mengwaga ye mebedi pele ba thoma kreiti 1 goba wona mphato wa pele.
tgt: ngenca yekutsi loku fundza lokusisekelo loku kumcoka emphumelelweni yemntfwana eminyakeni letako, umtsetfosivivinywa wekuchibiyela imitsetfo yetemfundvo lesisekelo lenyalo isephalamende ihlo ngota kutsi kuphoceleke kutsi bonkhe bantfwana batfole imfundvo yeecd yeminyaka lemibili ngembi kwekucala libanga lekucala.

src: ke gona mo fao bana ba swanetšego go rutwa, ba ithute ka meraloko le go fiwa setshola se ka bago se tee ka letšatši.
tgt: lesi ngiso sigaba lapho khona kufuneka bafundziswe ba ntfwana, bafundze babe badlala nekutsi lokungenani batfole sinye sidlo selusuku.

src: mohola wa disenthara tša go hlalefiša bomapimpa na ga se fela go thuša go lokišetša bana ba naga ya gaborena go atlega dikolong; gape di bohlokwa mo go ithomeleng kgwebo le mo go tlhomeng mešomo.
tgt: tikhungo tekutfutfukiswa kwebantfwana atilungiseleli kuphela kutsi bantfwana belive lakitsi labancane kutsi baphumelele esikolweni; tiphindze tibe ngumtfombo lomcoka wetemabhizinisi newekuvula ematfuba emisebenti.

src: disenthara tše ke karolo ye bohlokwa ya go hlohleletša ikonomi ya go kgathalelana.
tgt: letikhungo tiyi ncenye lebalulekile yemnotfo wekunakekela.

src: di thuša go tšwetšapele mekgwa ye batho ba iphedišago ka yona, kudududu basading, gomme se sa thuša go hloma mešomo ditšhabeng tše ntši.
tgt: tisimamisa tindlela tekutiphilisa, ka khulu kubomake, lekuyindle la leyengeta ekwakheni ema tfuba emsebenti emima ngweni leminengi.

src: nakong ya ge leuba la covid19 le aparela naga, disenthara tša ecd di ile tša amega gampe.
tgt: ngalesikhatsi sihlaselwa ngulobhubhane wecovi d19, tikhungo teecd tasha yeka kakhulu.

src: dise nthara tšeo di tshepetšego ditefong tša dikolo gore di šome di ile tša šitwa ke go lefela bašomedi ba tšona ebile batswadi ba bantši bao ba lahlegetšwego ke mešomo ba ile ba palelwa ke go ngwadiša bana ba bona.
tgt: tikhungo leti ncike kutindleko tekufundza kute tikhone kuhlala tisebenta betingakhoni kukhokhela basebenti bato futsi batali labanengi labalahlekelwa misebenti yabo bebanga khoni kugcina bantfwana babo bafundza kuletikhungo.

src: go rarolla seemo se, mmušo o ile wa hloma se khwama sa ecd sa kimollo le sa tlhomo ya mešomo go thuša disenthara tša ecd tšeo di lahlegetšwego ke meputso ka baka la leuba la covid19 go di kgontšha go kaonafala.
tgt: ngenca yaloko, hulumende wasungula sikhwama se ecd sesikhutsati sekuca shwa kwebantfu kute since dze tikhungo teecd leta lahlekelwa imali ngenca yalobhubhane nekutenta kutsi tikhone kuphindze tisebente.

src: go tlabela bana bao e lego badudi ba naga ye ka tsebo le mabokgoni ao ba a hlokago gore ba kgone go atlega bophelong ke maikarabelo ao ka moka ga rena re swanetšego go a šikara magetleng a rena.
tgt: kulungisa takhamuti takitsi letincane ngekutinika ema thulusi letiwadzingako kute tiphumelele emphilweni kungumsebenti lekufuneka siwutfwale sisonkhe.

src: re swanetše go tšwelapele go dira ka fao re ka kgonang ka gona, bjalo ka mmušo, lefapha la praebete le mekgatlo ya go hlabolla setšhaba, go thekga tlhalefišo ya bomapimpana.
tgt: kufu neka sichubeke kwenta konkhe lokusemandleni etfu, njengahulumende, simkhakha lotimele futsi si tinhlangano tekutfutfukisa, kusekela kutfutfukiswa kwe bantfwana.

src: ka ditirelo tša yona tše bohlokwa tše e di abago, go sa kgathale gore e ruta bana ba rena, e hlokomelela ba tswadi bao ba šomago bana goba e hloma mešomo go bahlomi ba dikgwebo, ecd e nale seabe se segolo kudu gore re kgone go fihlelela tše ntši tša dinepo tša rena tša tlhabollo.
tgt: ngalemisebenti yayo le mcoka leyiphakelako, noma kungaba kufundzisa ba ntfwana bakitsi, kuba nakekela kulabo batali labasebentako, noma kuvula ematfuba etemabhizinisi, iecd ifaka ligalelo lelikhulu ekuphumeleliseni letinhloso tetfu temigomo yentfutfuko.

src: ka fao o ka seketšago meetse ka gona more matshediso le ge kgoro ya meetse le tlhwekišo mengwa geng ya go feta e lekile ka maatla go fediša mošomo wo o bego o saletše morago wa go tsentšhetša badudi meetse, mo nageng ya afrika borwa ka bophara malapa, ao mebasepala e kgonnego go a tsentšhetša meetse a fihla go 68%.
tgt: indlela yekonga emanti more matshediso kuphakela emanti ngalokutsembe kile ngibomasipala kute afike kuyo yonkhe imindeni eningizimu afrika kuku68% kuphela, nanoma kunemitamo leyentiwe litiko letemanti netekutfutfwa kwendle kucedza kusalela emuva ekuphakeleni emanti kuleminyaka leyengcile.

src: motlatšatona wa meetse le tlhwekišo david mahlobo o bolela gore lebakakgolo la go hlola se ke mananeo kgoparara ao a tšofetšego, go hloka tlhokomelo le tokišo ya kgafetšakgafetša ditlamong tša meetse, le tlemagano ya go fokola magareng ga mananeo a dintlo le diprotšeke tša bjale tša tlhabollo ya mananeo kgoparara.
tgt: lisekela lendvuna yetemanti netekutfutfwa kwendle david mahlobo utsi loku kubangwa ngilesakhiwonchanti lesesigugile, kungasebenti kahle nekunganakekelwa kwemitfombo yemanti, kanye nekungahlangani kahle emkhatsini kwetinhlelo tetetindlu kanye nekwemiklamo yamanje yekutfutfukisa sakhiwonchanti.

src: "e tloga e le hlobaboroko ye kgolo gore kabo ya go botega ya meetse e laetša dika tša phuhlamo," a realo.
tgt: "kuyintfo lekhatsatako kutsi kuphakelwa kwemanti ngalokutsembekile kukhombisa timphawu tekuncipha," usho njalo.

src: bjalo ka naga ya go hlaelela meetse, afrika borwa ke karolo ya dinaga tše 30 tša komelelo lefaseng ka bophara.
tgt: njengelive lelingenawo emanti, iningizimu afrika ihlelenjiswe yaba kundzawo ye30 yemave langenamanti emhlabeni wonkhe.

src: bontši bja meetse a naga ye a tšwa dupuleng, eupša ka palo moka ye e kgonthišišitšwego ya dipula tšeo di lego fase ga 40% ge di bapetšwa le palomoka ya ngwaga ka ngwaga ya lefase ka bophara, naga ye e fela e angwa gampe ke komelelo.
tgt: emanti lamanyenti alelive atfolakala nakuna litulu, kodvwa ngenca yalelinani lelatiwako lemvula lelinciphe nge40% kunaleyo leyisilinganiso semnyaka yemhlaba, lelive livamise kuhlala lihlaselwa somiso.

src: le ge go le bjalo, kgoro e nale dikeletšo tše o ka di šomišago go seketša meetse.
tgt: nanoma kunjalo, litiko linetindlela letiticwayiso letibekelwe wena tekonga emanti.

src: go seketša meetse ka legaeng la gago goba ka kgwebong ya gago tswalela pompi ya meetse ge o hlapa sefahlego, o hlapa meno goba o kera ditedu.
tgt: tindlela tekonga emanti ekhaya noma ebhizinisini lakho vala imphompi uma ugeza buso, uchubha ematinyo noma ushefa.

src: go hlapa ka šawara tekano ya metsotso ye mehlano ka letšatši legatong la go hlapela ka pafong go šomiša fela kotara ya meetse ao a šomišwago ge o hlapela ka pafong, gomme o ka seketša dilithara tša go fihla 400 ka beke.
tgt: kusebentisa ishawa sikhatsi lesimizuzu lesihlanu ngelusuku kunekutsi ugeze ebhavini, konga emanti langafika kumalitha la400 ngeliviki.

src: go hlapa ka šawara go šomiša dilithara tša go fihla tše 20 tša meetse ka motsotso, mola ge o hlapela ka pafong o ka šomiša dili thara tše magareng ga 80 le 150 tša meetse ka pafo ye tee.
tgt: kugeza eshawa kungatsatsa emalitha emanti langafika ku20 ngemzuzu, kantsi kugeza ebhavini kungatsatsa emanti lasemkhatsini kwemalitha la80 kuya kula150 ngaleso sikhatsi kuphela.

src: ge o rata go hlapela ka pafong, o seke wa e tlatša ka mariba.
tgt: uma ukhetsa kugeza ebhavini, ungaligcwalisi.

src: efoga go folaša thwaelete fao go sego maleba.
tgt: gwema kuflasha emanti emthoyi kungenasidzingo.

src: lahlela dithišu, dikhunkhwane le dilahlwa tše dingwe ka gare ga setšhelo sa ditlakala e sego ka thwaelete.
tgt: lahla emathishu, tinambutane naletinye tintfo longasatidzingi etibini kunekutsi utilahlele emthoyi.

src: nako le nako ge o folaša, o šomiša meetse a go lekana dilithara tše 12. lokiša thwaelete ya go rothiša meetse go sego bjalo e tla senya meetse a go lekana dilithara tše 100 000 ka ngwaga.
tgt: ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi uma uflasha umthoyi, usebentisa emanti lamalitha la12.

src: šomiša meetse ao a šomišitšwego – meetse ao a šomileng go tšwa dipafong, metšheneng ya go hlatswa le methopong ye mengwe ya go bolokega go folaša thwaelete.
tgt: lungisa umthoyi lovutako uma ungenti njalo utawumosha emalitha emanti langafika ku100 000 ngemnyaka.

src: o seke wa tlatša letamo la boruthelo go feta tekano goba wa le hlwekiša ka go falatša meetse ka moka go feta tekano.
tgt: sebentisa "emanti langcolile" — emanti lasasebentile lasele uma ugeza ebhavini, emishinini yekuwasha kanye nakuleminye imitfombo lephephile kuflasha umthoyi wakho.

src: diketlele ga se tša swanela go tlatšwa ka meetse go feta tekano eupša di swanetše go tšhelwa fela meetse ao a lekanego gore o kgone go a šomiša.
tgt: ungayigcwalisi ngalokwecile noma ungayiwashi ngalokungenasidzingo indzawo yakho yekubhusha.

src: šomiša pakete go hlatswa koloi legatong la go šomiša phaephe.
tgt: ungagcwalisi emanti emagedleleni kodvwa awanele kufeza tidzingo takho.

src: ge e ba o gapeletšega go šomiša phaephe, diriša hlogwana ya go šašetša meetse yeo o ka kgonang go e tswalela ge o le gare o šašetša koloi ka yona.
tgt: sebentisa libhakede kunekutsi usebentise litfumbu lemanti kuhlanta imoto yakho.

src: ge o šomiša phaephe o ka diriša meetse a mantši a go fihla dilithara tše 30 ka motsotso.
tgt: uma kufuneka usebentise litfumbu, sebentisa sipreyi lesingasebenta kuvala emanti ngesikhatsi uwasha imoto.

src: balemi ba swanetše go netefatša gore ba beela kgole difotheladikhu khwane tše nago le mpholo kgole le methopo le meela ya meetse.
tgt: kusebentisa litfumbu lasengadzini kungatsatsa emanti langafika kumalitha emanti la30 ngemzuzu.

src: batho ba swanetše go bale tlhokomelo ye kgolo mafe long ao ba dulago go ona gore ba se tšhilafatše dinoka goba mariba a tšona.
tgt: balimi kufuneka bacinisekise kutsi imitsi yekubulala tinambutane ayifinyeleli emitfonjeni yemanti nakumifudlana.

src: go seketša meetse ka tšhengwaneng dula o nošetša dimela tša gago mesong goba mathapama, ge dithemphereitšha di fodile.
tgt: bantfu labahlala etindzaweni tasemakhaya akufuneki basebentise umfula noma ludvonga lemfula kutikhulula.

src: prep e ka kgona go thibela hiv vukuzenzele unnamed ge afrika borwa e tla be e gopola letšatši la lefase la aids ka la 1 manthole mmogo le matšatši a 16 a kgahlanong le dikgaruru tša bong (gbv) go tloga ka la 25 dibatsela go fihla ka la 10 manthole, vuk’uzenzele e lebelela kamano gareng ga gbv le hiv/aids.
tgt: iprep ingayivikela ihiv vukuzenzele unnamed njengobe ini ngizimu afrika itawube ikhu mbula lilanga lemhla ba lengculazi mhla lu1 ingongoni kanye nemalanga la16 ebushikashi ki bekulwa nebudlova lobucondziswe kubulili lobutsite (igbv), kusukela mhla tinge25 i mphala kuya ku mhla ti10 ingongoni, ivuk’uzenzele ibukisisa budlelwane lobukhona emkhatsini wegbv nehiv/aids.

src: sekhwama sa karabelo sa dikgaruru tša bong le polao ya basadi (gbvf) se nepile go netefatša gore afrika borwa ga e na dipolao tša basadi; bana; le batho ba go wela ka sehlopheng sa batho ba go ratana ka bong botee (lgbtqia+).
tgt: sikhwama lesibhekele bu dlova lobucondziswe kubulili lobutsite kanye nekubulawa kwebasikati (igbvf) si phokophele kucinisekisa kutsi iningizimu afrika ikhulule kile ayihlangabetani negbvf lecondziswe kubomake; bantfwana; besifazane labaya emacasini nebesifazane, labadvuna labaya emacasini nalabadvuna, bantfu laba bomphacambili, labantjintje bulili babo bemvelo, bantfu labanetitfo tebulili bobubili, bantfu lababukeka ngalokungakavami, labangafaki temacasi kanye nalabanye (ilgbtqia+).

src: sekhwama se tsebagaditšwe ke mopresidente cyril ramaphosa ka dibokwane 2022 go thekga phethagatšo ya leanotharollo la bosetšhaba go gbvf.
tgt: lesikhwama setfulwa ngu mengameli cyril ramaphosa ngendlovana nga2021, kwesekela kuphunyeleliswa kweluhlelo lwavelonkhe lwelisubuciko legbvf.

src: go ya le ka websaete ya sekhwama, sekhwama se se bapala karolo e bohlokwa ka go tlišeng phetogo, se itheile go dinyakišišo, ditemošo le thekgo go mekgatlo yeo e lwantšhanago le gbvf.
tgt: ngekuya kwewebhusa yithi yalesikhwama, sidlala indzima lebaluleke kakhulu ekwenteni kutsi tingucuko tenteke, ngekuya kwelu cwaningo, kucaphelisa kanye nekwesekelwa lokubonakalako lokunikwa tinhlangano leti sebenta ngalokubonakalako ekulweni negbvf.

src: wo mongwe wa mekgatlo yeo e thekgwago ke sekhwama se ke gugu dlamini foundation ya ka kwazulunatal yeo ka ngwaga wa 2022 e filwego r250 000 ke sekhwama sa kara belo ya gbvf.
tgt: lenye yaletinhlangano letesekelwa ngulesikhwama yigugu dlamini foundation ekwazulunatal, letfole r250 000 kusikhwama segbvf nga2022.

src: molaodiphethiši wa gugu dlamini foundation, mandisa mabaso, o hlomile mokgatlo wo ka 2010 morago ga gore mmagwe – mohu gugu dla mini – a bolawe ka go kgatlwa ka maswika ka 1998 ka durban morago ga go bolela gore o na le hiv .
tgt: umcondzisi lomkhulu wegugu dlamini foundation, mandisa mabaso, wasungula lenhlangano nga2010 nge muva kwekutsi make wakhe – longasekho emhlabeni gugu dlamini – wagcotjwa ngematje wate wafa nga1998 ethekwini ngenca yekutsi wadzalula kutsi unehiv .

src: "mokgatlo o ikemišeditše go matlafatša pušo ya selegae go kaonafatša karabelo ya gbvf, e lego sona selo se lego bohlokwa sa go tlo thuša go kgona go laola leuba la hiv ka afrika borwa," gwa realo mabaso.
tgt: "lenhlangano ihlose kucinisa telulawulo lwendzawo kute kwentiwe ncono indlela yeku bukana negbvf, lokubaluleke kakhulu ekuzuzeni lulawulo lwelubhubhane lwehiv eningizimu afrika," kusho mabaso.

src: "e tlo re thuša gape go fokotša diphetetšo tša hiv , go oketša phihlelelego ya go hwetša tlho komelo gape le go kaonafatša dipoelo tša maphelo bakeng sa basadi le banna bao ba fetetšwego ebile ba amilwego ke hiv/aids," a tlaleletša ka go realo.
tgt: "lokunye futsi lehlose ku kwenta kunciphisa kwesuleleka ngehiv/aids, kukhulisa kufinyelela kutekunakekelwa nekwenta kancono imiphu mela yetemphilo yebesifazane nalabadvuna labasulelekile nalabatsintfwa yihiv/aids," kwasho yena engeta.

src: mašeleng ao mokgatlo o a fiwago a thuša basadi le basetsana ba 522 255 le banna le bašemane ba 900 go tšwa mala peng ao a amilwego ke gbv le dikgaruru tša ka malapeng; batho ba go phela ka bogolofadi bao ba tlaišitšwego; le batho ba lgbtqia+, gwa realo mabaso.
tgt: lokwesekelwa ngetimali lokutfolwa ngulenhlangano kusita bomake nemantfombatana la522 255 kanye nemadvodza nebafana labange900 labavela emindenini letsintfwe yigbv kanye nebudlova basekhaya; bantfu labahlukunyetiwe labaphila nekukhubateka; kanye ne mmango welgbtqia+, kusho yena mabaso.

src: go ya ka unaids, ka mafelong ao hiv e tletšego kudu, basadi bao e lego batšwasehlabelo ba gbv ba lebagane le kgonagalo ya 50% ya gore ba tsenwe ke hiv .
tgt: ngekusho kweunaids, etindzaweni letinemtfwalo lomkhulu wehiv , bomake lababahlukunyetwa begbv bahlangabetana nematfuba lamakhulu langafika ku50% ekwesuleleka ngehiv .

src: a mangwe a mabaka a se ke go katwa, le banna ba go gana go šomiša dikhondomo.
tgt: letinye tizatfu taloku kugagadlela kanye nekwala kwemadvodza kuya emacasini asebentisa lijazi lemkhwenyana.

src: naa prep ke eng?
tgt: yini iprep?

src: ye nngwe ya ditsela tša go thibela phetetšo ya hiv ke go nwa preexposure prophylaxis (prep), e lego moriana woo o nwewago tšatši ka tšatši ke batho bao ba se nago hiv bao ba lego kotsing ya go fetelwa ka tsela ya thobalano goba go ihlabela ka diokobatši.
tgt: lenye yetindlela tekuvimba kwesuleleka ngehiv kunatsa ipreexposure prophylaxis (iprep), lokungemaphilisi lanatfwa onkhe emalanga bantfu labanehiv labasengotini lenkhulu yekwesuleleka ngehiv , ngekuya emacansini noma ngekusebentisa tidza kamiva lotijova ngato.

src: ka phato, tona joe phaahla o boletše gore afrika borwa e na le palo ya godimo ya tšhomišo ya prep ka afrika ya subsahara.
tgt: ngengci, indvuna joe phaahla utsite iningizimu afrika inelizinga leliphakeme leprep eafrika leseningizimu yesahara.

src: o rile mafelo a tlhokomelo ya maphelo a ka afrika borwa a dipersente tše 70 goba a 2 419 ka palo, a akareditše prep ka ditirelong tša ona tša ka mehla.
tgt: utsite tikhungo tetemphilo lesisekelo tase ningizimu afrika letinge70%, noma leti2 419, setifaka iprep lenatfwako kuluhlu lato le tinsita letinato.

src: "motho yoo a nwago prep ga a hloke go e nwa bophelo bja gagwe ka moka.
tgt: "bantfu labanatsa iprep abadzingi kutsi bayinatse timphilo tabo tonkhe, banga khetsa kuyinatsa ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi uma basengotini yekwesuleleka ngehiv .

src: a ka kgetha go e nwa nako le nako ge a le kotsing ya go ka fetelwa ke hiv .
tgt: nanoma kunjalo, kute kutsi iprep isebente kahle kakhulu, ifanele kutsi inatfwe onkhe emalanga [ngalesikhatsi]," kucinisekisa mabaso.

src: le ge go le bjalo, gore prep e šome ka tshwanelo, e swanetše e nwewe tšatši le lengwe le le lengwe [nakong yeo]," mabaso a netefatša ka go realo.
tgt: ifanele kutsi isetjentiswe kanye naletinye tindlela tekuvikela, njengemakhondomu ebesifazane noma alaba dvuna, ngoba iprep ayimvikeli umuntfu kuletinye tifo letitsatselwana emacansini kantsi futsi ayisiso sivikelantalo.

src: prep e swanetše e šomišwe le mekgwa ye mengwe ya thibelo e bjalo ka dikhondomo tša banna le tša basadi ka gore prep ga e šireletše motho kgahla nong le malwetši a mangwe a go fetela ka thobalano, gomme ebile ga se thibelapelego.
tgt: mabaso utsi etimeni lapho khona titsandzani tifuna kuba nemntfwana, iprep ingasita kuvikela kutsi umlingani lote ihiv angasuleleki ngehiv kanye nembungu.

src: mabaso o re ka mabakeng ao e lego gore baratani ba nyaka go ba le ngwana, prep e ka kgona go thuša go thibela phetetšo ya hiv go molekani yoo a se nago hiv mmogo le ngwana yo a sa imilwego.
tgt: nanoma kunjalo, ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, ku siphatsimandla sase ningizimu afrika lesilawula imikhicito yetemphilo sivume kusetjentiswa kweringi yesitfo sangasese sabomake (ivaginal ring) njengeprep .

src: go sa le bjalo, mathomong a ngwaga wo ba setheo sa taolo ya ditšweletšwa tša maphelo sa afrika borwa ba fetišitše tšhomišo ya rini ya setho sa bosadi bjalo ka prep .
tgt: leringi inemutsi losinca ndzagciwane lobitwa ngekutsi idapivirine futsi ifanele kutsi intjintjwe njalo ngenyanga.

src: rini yeo e na le pilisi ya antiretroviral yeo e bitšwago dapivirine, gomme yona e swanetše e fetolwe kgwedi ka kgwedi.
tgt: kwengeta, iprep lensha – umjovo lotsatsa tinyanga letimbili usemtimbeni – usalindzele kuvunywa.

src: go tlaleletša seo, prep ye mpsha, e lego tšhwaana yeo e dulago kgwedi tše pedi ka mmeleng wa motho, e sa emetše gore e fetišwe.
tgt: utawutsi ungavunywa, bantfu angeke basadzinga kutsi bakhu mbule kutsi banatse emaphilisi onkhe emalanga.

src: ge e se no fetišwa, batho ba ka se sa hloka go ikgopotša gore ba nwe pilisi tšatši ka tšatši.
tgt: kuya emacasini ngalokuphephilelenhlangano ihlose kunci phisa kwesuleleka ngehiv ngekukhutsata kusetjentiswa kwemakhondomu kanye nekuya emacasini ngaloku phephile.

src: thobalano yeo e bolokegilego mokgatlo wo o ikemišeditše go fokotša diphetetšo tša hiv ka go tšweletša pele tšhomišo ya dikhondomo le thobalano yeo e bolokegilego.
tgt: "sicela bantfwana nelu sha kutsi bangasheshi baye emacansini kute kutsi kube sikhatsi sekutsi bakhone kutitsatsela tincumo letibhadlile naletinemphilo," kusho mabaso.

src: seo bommagobana bao ba nago le hiv gomme ba nyantshago ba swanetsego go se tseba vukuzenzele unnamed ge afrika borwa e tla be e dira segopotšo sa letšatši la lefase la aids ka la 1 manthole, kgoro ya maphelo ka kwazulunatal e eleditše bommagobana bao ba nago le hiv gore ba fepe masea a bona ka go a nyantšha feela tekano ya dikgwedi tše tshela.
tgt: bomake labanehiv labamunyisako lokufanele kutsi bakwati vukuzenzele unnamed njengoba ini ngizimu afrika itawube ibungata lilanga lemhlaba le ngculazi mhla lu1 nge ngongoni, litiko lete mphilo lakwazulunatal selicaphelise ngeku tsi bomake labanehiv labamunyisako kutsi bacabange ngekumunyisa libele kuphela bantfwana babo tinyanga letisi tfupha.

src: go ya ka kgoro, ge eba o mosadi yoo a nyantšhago gomme ebile o na le hiv , go bohlokwa gore o boledišane le mothobamatswalo wa gago wa tša hiv ka mehuta ya go fepa.
tgt: ngekuya kwelitiko, uma ngabe ungumake lonehiv kantsi futsi uyamunyisa, kubalulekile kukhulumisana nemeluleki wakho wetehiv ngetindlela tekumunyisa.

src: ge e ba o kgetha go nyantšha, netefatša gore o fepa ngwana ka go mo nyantšha feela tekano ya dikgwedi tše tshela tša mathomo.
tgt: uma ngabe ukhetsa kumunyisa libele, yenta siciniseko sekutsi umunyisa libele kuphela tinyanga letisitfupha.

src: diphatišišo di bontšhitše gore go na le kgonagalo e nnyane kudu ya gore ngwana a fetelwe ke hiv go tšwa matutung a letswele ge eba mmagwe a mo fepa ka go mo nyantšha feela.
tgt: lucwaningo lukhombisa kutsi mancane kakhulu ematfuba ekutsi luswane lungatfola ihiv elubisini lwelibele lamake uma ngabe make amunyisa libele kuphela tinyanga letisitfupha.

src: mo dikgweding tšeo o tla bego o imile, le ge o tla be o nyantšha, netefatša gore o šomiša khondomo ge o tsenela tša thobalano gore o thibele diphetetšo tše diswa.
tgt: kuletinyanga ukhulelwe, kanye nekumunyisa libele, yenta siciniseko sekutsi usebentisa ikhondomu uma uya emacasini kute kutsi uvikele kutsi lesifo siphindze futsi sikungene.

src: ge eba o na le mathata afe goba afe a bjalo ka ditlhoko tše bohloko goba matswele a bohloko, netefatša gore o ya kliniking e sa le ka pela go yo hwetša thušo.
tgt: uma ngabe unenkinga njengekuba buhlungu kwetingono noma emabele, yenta siciniseko sekutsi usheshe uye emtfolamphilo uyotfola lusito.

src: kgoro e tloga e gatelela taba ya go fepa ka go nyantšha feela ka ge e thuša ngwana gore a be le mašole a mmele a tiilego, gape le go hlama kgokagano e tiilego gareng ga mma le ngwana.
tgt: litiko lincoma kakhulu kumunyisa libele kuphela ngoba kusita luswane kutsi lube nemasotja emtimba lacinile, kanye nebudlelwane lobucinile emkhatsini wamake nemntfwana.

src: go nyantšha go fokotša gape le dikotsi tša go tsenwa ke kankere ya letswele.
tgt: kumunyisa libele kuphindze futsi kunciphise bungoti bamake bekutsi abe namdlavuta wemabele.

src: dikakanyo tša maaka le dinnete mabapi le go nyantšha go na le dikakanyo tša maaka tše ntšhi tša mabapi le go nyantšha.
tgt: emanga nemacini so mayelana neku munyisa kunemanga lamanyenti mayelana nekumunyisa libele, litikoke liwacitsile lamanga ngekuphendvula lemibuto lelandzelako levame kubutwa bomake labanehiv kanye nalabo labete ihiv .

src: kgoro e ile ya phošolla dikakanyo tša maaka tše ka go araba dipotšišo tše latelago tša go botšišwa ka mehla ke bommagobana bao ba nago le hiv mmogo le bao ba se nago nayo.
tgt: umbuto: makhelwane wami utsi kufanele kutsi ngitfole umutsi wekuhlanta sisu semntfwanami.

src: naa se se bohlokwa?
tgt: kubalulekile yini loku?

src: karabo: matutu a mathomo, ao a tšweletšwago ke dithaka tša maswi morago ga pelego, a hlwekiša ditšhila go tšwa mpeng ya ngwana.
tgt: imphendvulo: umtfubi, lokulubisi lwekucala lweli bele lukhishwa ngemadlala lasemabeleni ngemuva kwekubeleka, luhlanta emangcoliso ekucalangca esiswini seluswane.
